msgstr "Interagere med indlæg"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:326
msgid "Different actions are possible on a post."
msgstr "Forskellige handlinger er mulige på et indlæg."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:328
msgid ""
"Mark a question as **favorite** by clicking the star button (:guilabel:`☆`)."
msgstr ""
"Markér et spørgsmål som **favorit** ved at klikke på stjerneknappen "
"(:guilabel:`☆`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:329
msgid ""
"Follow a post and get **notifications** (by email or within Odoo) when it is "
"answered by clicking the bell button (:guilabel:`🔔`)."
msgstr ""
"Følg et indlæg og modtag **notifikationer** (via e-mail eller i Odoo), når "
"det besvares, ved at klikke på klokkeknappen (:guilabel:`🔔`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:331
msgid ""
"**Vote** *for* (up arrow :guilabel:`▲`) or *against* (down "
"arrow :guilabel:`▼`) a question or answer."
msgstr ""
"**Stem** *for* (pil op :guilabel:`▲`) eller *imod* (pil ned :guilabel:`▼`) "
"et spørgsmål eller svar."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:333
msgid ""
"Mark an answer as **best** by clicking the check mark button "
"(:guilabel:`✔`). This option is only available if the :guilabel:`Forum Mode` "
"is set to :guilabel:`Questions`."
msgstr ""
"Markér et svar som **bedst** ved at klikke på fluebensknappen (:guilabel:`✔`)"
". Denne mulighed er kun tilgængelig, hvis :guilabel:`Forum-tilstand` er sat "
"til :guilabel:`Spørgsmål`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:335
msgid ":guilabel:`Answer` a question."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Besvar` et spørgsmål."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:336
msgid ""
"**Comment** on a question or answer by clicking the speech bubble button "
"(:guilabel:`💬`)."
msgstr ""
"**Kommentér** på et spørgsmål eller svar ved at klikke på taleboblen "
"(:guilabel:`💬`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:337
msgid ""
"**Share** a question on Facebook, Twitter, or LinkedIn by clicking the "
"*share nodes* button."
msgstr ""
"**Del** et spørgsmål på Facebook, Twitter eller LinkedIn ved at klikke på "
"*delingsknappen*."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:339
msgid "Click the ellipsis button (:guilabel:`...`) to:"
msgstr "Klik på ellipseknappen (:guilabel:`...`) for at:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:341
msgid ":guilabel:`Edit` a question or answer."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Redigere` et spørgsmål eller svar."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:342
msgid ":guilabel:`Close` a question."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Lukke` et spørgsmål."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:343
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delete` a question, answer, or comment. It is possible "
"to :guilabel:`Undelete` questions afterward."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Slette` et spørgsmål, svar eller kommentar. Det er muligt at "
":guilabel:`Fortryde sletning` af spørgsmål bagefter."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:345
msgid ":guilabel:`Flag` a question or answer as offensive."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Rapportere` et spørgsmål eller svar som stødende."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:346
msgid ":guilabel:`Convert` a comment into an answer."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Konvertere` en kommentar til et svar."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:347
msgid ""
":guilabel:`View` the related :ref:`Helpdesk ticket <helpdesk/forum>`, if any."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vise` den relaterede :ref:`Kundeservice-sag <helpdesk/forum>`, "
"hvis der er en."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:None
msgid "Posts actions"
msgstr "Indlægshandlinger"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:353
msgid ""
"By default, 150 karma points are required to view another user's profile. "
"This value can be configured when creating a new website."
msgstr ""
"Som standard kræves der 150 karmapoint for at se en anden brugers profil. "
"Denne værdi kan konfigureres, når der oprettes en ny hjemmeside."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:359
msgid "Moderate a forum"
msgstr "Moderer et forum"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:361
msgid ""
"On the forum's front end, the sidebar's :guilabel:`Moderation tools` section "
"gathers the essential moderator functionalities."
msgstr ""
"På forummets frontend samler sidebjalkens :guilabel:`Modereringsværktøjer`-"
"sektion de essentielle moderatorfunktioner."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:None
msgid "Forum sidebar moderation tools"
msgstr "Modereringsværktøjer i forumets sidebjalk"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:367
msgid ""
":guilabel:`To Validate`: access all questions and answers waiting for "
"validation before being displayed to non-moderator users."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Til validering`: Tilgå alle spørgsmål og svar, der venter på "
"validering, før de vises til brugere uden moderatorrettigheder."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:None
msgid "Question to validate"
msgstr "Spørgsmål der skal valideres"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:374
msgid ""
"A question is pending if a user does not have the required karma. The user "
"is not able to post questions or answers while awaiting validation. Only one "
"pending question per user is allowed per forum."
msgstr ""
"Et spørgsmål er afventende, hvis en bruger ikke har de nødvendige "
"karmapoint. Brugeren kan ikke offentliggøre spørgsmål eller svar, mens "
"vedkommende afventer validering. Kun ét afventende spørgsmål pr. bruger er "
"tilladt pr. forum."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:378
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Flagged`: access all questions and answers that have been flagged "
"as offensive. Click :guilabel:`Accept` to remove the offensive flag "
"or :guilabel:`Offensive` to confirm it, then select a reason and "
"click :guilabel:`Mark as offensive`. The post is then hidden from users "
"without moderation rights, and 100 karma points are deducted from the "
"offending user's tally."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Markeret`: Tilgå alle spørgsmål og svar, der er blevet markeret "
"som stødende. Klik på :guilabel:`Accepter` for at fjerne den stødende "
"markering eller :guilabel:`Stødende` for at bekræfte den, vælg derefter en "
"grund, og klik på :guilabel:`Marker som stødende`. Indlægget skjules "
"derefter for brugere uden moderatorrettigheder, og 100 karmapoint fratrækkes "
"den krænkende brugers konto."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:None
msgid "Offensive reason selection"
msgstr "Valg af stødende årsag"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:386
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Closed`: access all questions that have been closed. It is "
"possible to :guilabel:`Delete` or :guilabel:`Reopen` them. To close a "
"question, open it, click the ellipsis button (:guilabel:`...`), "
"then :guilabel:`Close`, select a :guilabel:`Close Reason`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Close post`. The post is then hidden from users without "
"moderation rights."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Lukket`: Tilgå alle spørgsmål, der er blevet lukket. Det er "
"muligt at :guilabel:`Slette` eller :guilabel:`Genåbne` dem. For at lukke et "
"spørgsmål skal du åbne det, klikke på ellipseknappen (:guilabel:`...`), "
"derefter :guilabel:`Luk`, vælge en :guilabel:`Lukningsårsag` og klikke på "
":guilabel:`Luk indlæg`. Indlægget skjules derefter for brugere uden "
"moderatorrettigheder."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:392
msgid ""
"When selecting :guilabel:`Spam or advertising` or :guilabel:`Contains "
"offensive or malicious remarks` as the reason, 100 karma points are deducted "
"from the poster's tally."
msgstr ""
"Når du vælger :guilabel:`Spam eller reklame` eller :guilabel:`Indeholder "
"stødende eller ondsindede bemærkninger` som årsag, fratrækkes 100 karmapoint "
"fra forfatterens konto."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:396
msgid ""
"Create and edit close reasons by going to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Forum: Close Reasons`. Select :guilabel:`Basic` "
"as :guilabel:`Reason Type` if the reason should be used when closing a "
"question, and :guilabel:`Offensive` if it should be used for flagged posts."
msgstr ""
"Opret og rediger lukningsårsager ved at gå til "
":menuselection:`Hjemmeside --> Konfiguration --> Forum: Lukningsårsager`. "
"Vælg :guilabel:`Grundlæggende` som :guilabel:`Årsagstype`, hvis årsagen skal "
"bruges ved lukning af et spørgsmål, og :guilabel:`Stødende`, hvis den skal "
"bruges til markerede indlæg."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:399
msgid ""
"Manage all posts by going to :menuselection:`Website  --> Configuration --> "
"Forum: Forums`, selecting the forum, and clicking the :guilabel:`Posts` "
"smart button. By clicking the :guilabel:`Actions` button, it is possible "
"to :guilabel:`Export`, :guilabel:`Archive`, :guilabel:`Unarchive`, "
"or :guilabel:`Delete` one or multiple posts."
msgstr ""
"Administrer alle indlæg ved at gå til :menuselection:`Hjemmeside --> "
"Konfiguration --> Forum: Fora`, vælg forummet og klik på :guilabel:`Indlæg`-"
"smartknappen. Ved at klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Handlinger` er det muligt "
"at :guilabel:`Eksportere`, :guilabel:`Arkivere`, :guilabel:`Gendan fra "
"arkiv` eller :guilabel:`Slette` et eller flere indlæg."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:5
msgid "Live Chat"
msgstr "Live Chat"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo **Live Chat** allows users to communicate with website visitors in real-"
"time. With **Live Chat**, leads can be qualified for their sales potential, "
"support questions can be answered in real time, and issues can be directed "
"to the appropriate team for further investigation or follow up. **Live "
"Chat** also provides the opportunity for instant feedback from customers."
msgstr ""
"Odoo **Live Chat** gør det muligt for brugere at kommunikere med "
"hjemmesidebesøgende i realtid. Med **Live Chat** kan leads kvalificeres for "
"deres salgspotentiale, supportspørgsmål kan besvares i realtid, og problemer "
"kan dirigeres til det relevante team for yderligere undersøgelse eller "
"opfølgning. **Live Chat** giver også mulighed for øjeblikkelig feedback fra "
"kunder."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:13
msgid "Enable Live Chat"
msgstr "Aktivér Live Chat"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:15
msgid "The **Live Chat** application can be installed multiple ways:"
msgstr "**Live Chat**-applikationen kan installeres på flere måder:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:17
msgid ""
"Go to the :menuselection:`Apps application`, search `Live Chat`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Install`."
msgstr ""
"Gå til :menuselection:`Apps-applikationen`, søg efter `Live Chat`, og klik "
"på :guilabel:`Installér`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:18
msgid ""
"Go to the :menuselection:`Helpdesk app --> Configuration --> Helpdesk Teams` "
"list view, select a team, and on the team's settings page, click the "
"checkbox next to :guilabel:`Live Chat`, under the :guilabel:`Channels` "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Gå til :menuselection:`Kundeservice-appen --> Konfiguration --> Kundeservice-"
"teams` listevisning, vælg et team, og på teamets indstillingsside skal du "
"klikke på afkrydsningsfeltet ved siden af :guilabel:`Live Chat` under "
"sektionen :guilabel:`Kanaler`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:21
msgid ""
"In the :menuselection:`Website` app, go to :menuselection:`Configuration --> "
"Settings`, scroll to the :guilabel:`Email & Marketing` section, check the "
"box next to :guilabel:`Livechat`, and click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"I :menuselection:`Hjemmeside`-appen skal du gå til "
":menuselection:`Konfiguration --> Indstillinger`, rulle ned til sektionen "
":guilabel:`E-mail og marketing`, markere feltet ved siden af "
":guilabel:`Livechat` og klikke på :guilabel:`Gem`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:0
msgid "View of the settings page and the live chat feature for Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr ""
"Visning af indstillingssiden og live chat-funktionen til Odoo Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:29
msgid ""
"After the **Live Chat** application is installed, a live chat *Channel* is "
"created, by default."
msgstr ""
"Efter **Live Chat**-applikationen er installeret, oprettes en live chat-"
"*kanal* som standard."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:32
msgid "Create live chat channels"
msgstr "Opret live chat-kanaler"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:34
msgid ""
"To create a new live chat *Channel*, go to the :menuselection:`Live Chat "
"app`. Then, click :guilabel:`New` to open a blank channel detail form. Enter "
"the name of the new channel in the :guilabel:`Channel Name` field."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en ny live chat-*kanal*, gå til :menuselection:`Live Chat-"
"appen`. Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Ny` for at åbne en tom "
"kanaldetaljeformular. Indtast navnet på den nye kanal i feltet "
":guilabel:`Kanalnavn`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:38
msgid ""
"To configure the remaining tabs on the channel detail form (:ref:`Operators "
"<livechat/operators-tab>`, :ref:`Options <livechat/options-"
"tab>`, :ref:`Channel Rules <livechat/channel-rules-tab>`, and :ref:`Widget "
"<livechat/widget-tab>`), follow the steps below."
msgstr ""
"For at konfigurere de resterende faner på kanaldetaljeformularen "
"(:ref:`Operatører <livechat/operators-tab>`, :ref:`Indstillinger <livechat/"
"options-tab>`, :ref:`Kanalregler <livechat/channel-rules-tab>` og "
":ref:`Widget <livechat/widget-tab>`), følg trinene nedenfor."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:None
msgid "View of a live chat channel form for Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr "Visning af en live chat-kanalformular til Odoo Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:46
msgid ""
"The channel detail form for any channel can be accessed by navigating back "
"to the :guilabel:`Website Live Chat Channels` dashboard, via the "
"breadcrumbs. Find the Kanban card for the appropriate live chat channel, "
"hover over it, and then click on the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-"
"v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` icon to open the drop-down menu. "
"Click :guilabel:`Configure Channel` to open the channel detail form."
msgstr ""
"Kanaldetaljeformularen for enhver kanal kan tilgås ved at navigere tilbage "
"til :guilabel:`Hjemmeside Live Chat-kanaler` dashboard via brødkrummerne. "
"Find Kanban-kortet for den relevante live chat-kanal, hold musen over det, "
"og klik derefter på :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(lodret ellipse)`-"
"ikonet for at åbne rullemenuen. Klik på :guilabel:`Konfigurer kanal` for at "
"åbne kanaldetaljeformularen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:55
msgid "Operators tab"
msgstr "Záložka operátoři"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:57
msgid ""
"*Operators* are the users who act as agents and respond to live chat "
"requests from customers. When a user is added as an operator in a live chat "
"channel, they can receive chats from website visitors wherever they are in "
"the database. Chat windows open in the bottom-right corner of the screen."
msgstr ""
"*Operatører* er de brugere, der fungerer som agenter og besvarer live chat-"
"anmodninger fra kunder. Når en bruger tilføjes som operatør i en live chat-"
"kanal, kan vedkommende modtage chats fra hjemmesidebesøgende uanset hvor i "
"databasen de befinder sig. Chatvinduer åbnes i nederste højre hjørne af "
"skærmen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:None
msgid "A live chat pop-up window in an Odoo database."
msgstr "Et live chat-pop op-vindue i en Odoo-database."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:64
msgid ""
"On the channel detail form, click the :guilabel:`Operators` tab. The user "
"who originally created the live chat channel has been added as an operator "
"by default."
msgstr ""
"På kanaldetaljeformularen klik på fanen :guilabel:`Operatører`. Brugeren, "
"der oprindeligt oprettede live chat-kanalen, er blevet tilføjet som operatør "
"som standard."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:68
msgid ""
"Current operators can be edited, or removed, by clicking on their respective "
"boxes in the :guilabel:`Operators` tab, which reveals a "
"separate :guilabel:`Open: Operators` pop-up. In that pop-up, adjust any "
"information, as needed. Then, click :guilabel:`Save`, or "
"click :guilabel:`Remove` to remove that operator from the channel."
msgstr ""
"Nuværende operatører kan redigeres eller fjernes ved at klikke på deres "
"respektive bokse i fanen :guilabel:`Operatører`, hvilket åbner en separat "
":guilabel:`Åbn: Operatører`-pop op. I den pop op justeres eventuelle "
"oplysninger efter behov. Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Gem`, eller klik på "
":guilabel:`Fjern` for at fjerne den pågældende operatør fra kanalen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:73
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Add` to reveal an :guilabel:`Add: Operators` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Tilføj` for at åbne et :guilabel:`Tilføj: Operatører`-pop "
"op-vindue."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:75
msgid ""
"In the pop-up window, scroll to find the desired users, or enter their name "
"in the search bar. Then, tick the checkbox next to the users to be added, "
"and click :guilabel:`Select`."
msgstr ""
"I pop op-vinduet rul for at finde de ønskede brugere, eller indtast deres "
"navn i søgefeltet. Sæt derefter flueben ved de brugere, der skal tilføjes, "
"og klik på :guilabel:`Vælg`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:78
msgid ""
"New operators can be created and added to the list directly from this pop-up "
"window, as well, by clicking :guilabel:`New`, and filling out "
"the :guilabel:`Create Operators` form. When the form is complete, "
"click :guilabel:`Save & Close`, or :guilabel:`Save & New` for multiple "
"record creations."
msgstr ""
"Nye operatører kan også oprettes og tilføjes til listen direkte fra dette "
"pop op-vindue ved at klikke på :guilabel:`Ny` og udfylde formularen "
":guilabel:`Opret operatører`. Når formularen er udfyldt, klik på "
":guilabel:`Gem & luk` eller :guilabel:`Gem & ny` for at oprette flere poster."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:83
msgid ""
"Creating a new user can impact the status of an Odoo subscription, as the "
"total number of users in a database counts towards the billing rate. Proceed "
"with caution before creating a new user. If a user already exists, adding "
"them as an operator will **not** alter the subscription or billing rate for "
"a database."
msgstr ""
"Vytvoření nového uživatele může ovlivnit stav předplatného Odoo, protože "
"celkový počet uživatelů v databázi se započítává do fakturační sazby. Před "
"vytvořením nového uživatele postupujte opatrně. Pokud uživatel již existuje, "
"jeho přidání jako operátora **nezmění** předplatné ani fakturační sazbu pro "
"databázi."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:93
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Options` tab on the live chat channel detail form contains "
"the visual and text settings for the live chat window."
msgstr ""
"Fanen :guilabel:`Indstillinger` på live chat-kanalens detaljeformular "
"indeholder de visuelle indstillinger og tekstindstillinger for live chat-"
"vinduet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:99
msgid "Livechat button"
msgstr "Livechat-knap"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:101
msgid ""
"The *Livechat Button* is the icon that appears in the bottom-right corner of "
"the website."
msgstr ""
"*Livechat-knappen* er ikonet, der vises i nederste højre hjørne af "
"hjemmesiden."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:103
msgid ""
"Change the text in the :guilabel:`Notification text` field to update the "
"greeting displayed in the text bubble when the live chat button appears on "
"the website."
msgstr ""
"Rediger teksten i feltet :guilabel:`Meddelelsetekst` for at opdatere "
"hilsenen, der vises i tekstboblen, når live chat-knappen vises på "
"hjemmesiden."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:106
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Livechat Button Color` alters the color of the live chat "
"button as it appears on the website. To change the color, click on a color "
"bubble to open the color selection window, then click and drag the circle "
"along the color gradient. Click out of the selection window once complete. "
"Click the :icon:`fa-refresh` :guilabel:`(refresh)` icon to the right of the "
"color bubbles to reset the colors to the default selection."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Livechat-knapfarve` ændrer farven på live chat-knappen, som den "
"vises på hjemmesiden. For at ændre farven klik på en farveboble for at åbne "
"farvevælgervinduet, klik og træk derefter cirklen langs farvegradienten. "
"Klik ud af vælgervinduet, når du er færdig. Klik på :icon:`fa-refresh` "
":guilabel:`(opdater)`-ikonet til højre for farveboblerne for at nulstille "
"farverne til standardvalget."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:113
msgid ""
"Color selection, for the button or header, can be made manually using a "
"slider or through RGB, HSL, or HEX color code entries from the pop-up color "
"selection window that appears when either of the color bubbles are clicked. "
"Different options are available, depending on the operating system."
msgstr ""
"Valg af farve til knappen eller headeren kan foretages manuelt ved hjælp af "
"en skyder eller gennem RGB-, HSL- eller HEX-farvekodeindtastninger fra popup-"
"vinduet til farvevalg, der vises, når der klikkes på en af farveboblerne. "
"Forskellige muligheder er tilgængelige afhængigt af operativsystemet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:119
msgid ""
"With the following settings, the live chat button appears on the website as "
"shown:"
msgstr ""
"Med følgende indstillinger vises live chat-knappen på hjemmesiden som vist:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:121
msgid ":guilabel:`Notification text`: \"Have a Question? Chat with us.\""
msgstr ":guilabel:`Notification text`: \"Har du et spørgsmål? Chat med os.\""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:122
msgid ":guilabel:`Livechat Button Color`: set to purple"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Livechat Button Color`: indstillet til lilla"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:0
msgid "View of an Odoo website emphasizing the livechat button."
msgstr "Visning af en Odoo-hjemmeside med fremhævelse af livechat-knappen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:128
msgid "Livechat window"
msgstr "Livechat-vindue"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:130
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Livechat Window` is the space where the live chat "
"conversation with website visitors takes place."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Livechat Window` er det område, hvor live chat-samtalen med "
"besøgende på hjemmesiden finder sted."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:133
msgid ""
"Edit the :guilabel:`Welcome Message` to change the message a visitor sees "
"when they open a new chat session. This message appears as though it is sent "
"by a live chat operator, and acts as both a greeting and an invitation to "
"continue the conversation."
msgstr ""
"Redigér :guilabel:`Welcome Message` for at ændre den besked, en besøgende "
"ser, når de åbner en ny chatsession. Denne besked vises, som om den er sendt "
"af en live chat-operatør, og fungerer både som en hilsen og en invitation "
"til at fortsætte samtalen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:137
msgid ""
"Edit the :guilabel:`Chat Input Placeholder` to alter the text that appears "
"in the box where visitors type their replies. This message prompts the "
"visitor to initiate the chat."
msgstr ""
"Redigér :guilabel:`Chat Input Placeholder` for at ændre den tekst, der vises "
"i boksen, hvor besøgende skriver deres svar. Denne besked opfordrer den "
"besøgende til at starte chatten."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:140
msgid ""
"The *Channel Header* is the colored bar at the top of the chat window. "
"The :guilabel:`Channel Header Color` can be changed following the same steps "
"as the :ref:`Livechat button <livechat/livechat-button>`."
msgstr ""
"*Channel Header* er den farvede bjælke øverst i chatvinduet. "
":guilabel:`Channel Header Color` kan ændres ved at følge de samme trin som "
"for :ref:`Livechat button <livechat/livechat-button>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:147
msgid "The live chat window with a purple channel header and placeholder text."
msgstr "Live chat-vinduet med en lilla channel header og pladsholdertekst."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:147
msgid ""
"The live chat window with a purple channel header and placeholder text that "
"reads, \"Say Something...\""
msgstr ""
"Live chat-vinduet med en lilla channel header og pladsholdertekst, der lyder "
"\"Sig noget...\""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:153
msgid "Channel Rules tab"
msgstr "Fanen Kanalregler"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:155
msgid ""
"To configure which website user actions open the live chat window, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Channel Rules` tab on the live chat channel detail form."
msgstr ""
"For at konfigurere hvilke handlinger fra hjemmesidens brugere der åbner live "
"chat-vinduet, gå til fanen :guilabel:`Channel Rules` på live chat-kanalens "
"detailformular."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:158
msgid ""
"To create a new channel rule, click :guilabel:`Add a line`. This opens "
"the :guilabel:`Create Rules` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en ny kanalregel skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Add a line`. "
"Dette åbner popup-vinduet :guilabel:`Create Rules`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:None
msgid "View of a channel's rules form for Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr "Visning af en kanals regelformular til Odoo Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:165
msgid "Create new rules"
msgstr "Opret nye regler"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:167
msgid ""
"Fill out the fields on the :guilabel:`Create Rules` pop-up window as "
"instructed below, then click :guilabel:`Save & Close`."
msgstr ""
"Udfyld felterne i popup-vinduet :guilabel:`Create Rules` som anvist "
"nedenfor, og klik derefter på :guilabel:`Save & Close`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:172
msgid "Live Chat Button"
msgstr "LiveChat-knap"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:174
msgid ""
"The *Livechat Button* is the icon that appears in the bottom-right corner of "
"the website. Select from one of the following display options:"
msgstr ""
"*Livechat Button* er ikonet, der vises i nederste højre hjørne af "
"hjemmesiden. Vælg en af følgende visningsmuligheder:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:177
msgid ":guilabel:`Show`: displays the chat button on the page."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Show`: viser chatknappen på siden."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:178
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Show with notification`: displays the chat button, as well as a "
"floating text bubble next to the button."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vis med meddelelse`: viser chatknappen samt en flydende "
"tekstboble ved siden af knappen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:180
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Open automatically`: displays the button, and automatically opens "
"the chat window after a specified amount of time (designated in "
"the :guilabel:`Open automatically timer` field, that appears when this "
"option is selected)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Åbn automatisk`: viser knappen og åbner automatisk chatvinduet "
"efter en angivet tid (angivet i feltet :guilabel:`Åbn automatisk timer`, der "
"vises, når denne mulighed vælges)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:183
msgid ":guilabel:`Hide`: hides the chat button on the page."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Skjul`: skjuler chatknappen på siden."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:185
msgid "Chatbot"
msgstr "Chatbot"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:187
msgid ""
"To include a :doc:`Chatbot <livechat/chatbots>` on this channel, select it "
"from the drop-down menu. If the chatbot should only be active when no "
"operators are active, check the box labeled :guilabel:`Enabled only if no "
"operator`."
msgstr ""
"For at inkludere en :doc:`Chatbot <livechat/chatbots>` på denne kanal skal "
"du vælge den fra rullemenuen. Hvis chatbotten kun skal være aktiv, når ingen "
"operatører er aktive, skal du markere feltet :guilabel:`Kun aktiveret, hvis "
"ingen operatør`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:191
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Enabled only if no operator` field is **only** visible if a "
"chatbot is selected in the :guilabel:`Chatbot` field."
msgstr ""
"Feltet :guilabel:`Kun aktiveret, hvis ingen operatør` er **kun** synligt, "
"hvis en chatbot er valgt i feltet :guilabel:`Chatbot`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:194
msgid "URL Regex"
msgstr "URL Regex"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:196
msgid ""
"The *URL Regex* specifies the web pages where this rule should be applied. "
"In the :guilabel:`URL Regex` field, input the relative URL of the page where "
"the chat button should appear."
msgstr ""
"*URL Regex* angiver de websider, hvor denne regel skal anvendes. I feltet "
":guilabel:`URL Regex` skal du indtaste den relative URL for siden, hvor "
"chatknappen skal vises."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:200
msgid ""
"For example, to apply the rule to the URL, `https://mydatabse.odoo.com/"
"shop`, enter `/shop` to the :guilabel:`URL Regex` field."
msgstr ""
"For at anvende reglen på URL'en `https://mydatabse.odoo.com/shop` skal du "
"indtaste `/shop` i feltet :guilabel:`URL Regex`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:203
msgid ""
"To apply the rule to *all* pages on the database, enter `/` in "
"the :guilabel:`URL Regex` field."
msgstr ""
"For at anvende reglen på *alle* sider i databasen skal du indtaste `/` i "
"feltet :guilabel:`URL Regex`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:206
msgid "Open automatically timer"
msgstr "Åbn automatisk timer"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:208
msgid ""
"This field designates the amount of time (in seconds) a page should be open "
"before the chat window opens. This field **only** appears if "
"the :guilabel:`Live Chat Button` for this rule is set to :guilabel:`Open "
"automatically`."
msgstr ""
"Dette felt angiver mængden af tid (i sekunder), en side skal være åben, før "
"chatvinduet åbnes. Dette felt vises **kun**, hvis :guilabel:`Live Chat-knap` "
"for denne regel er indstillet til :guilabel:`Åbn automatisk`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:212
msgid "Country"
msgstr "Land"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:214
msgid ""
"If this channel should **only** be available to site visitors in specific "
"countries, add them to the :guilabel:`Country` field. If this field is left "
"blank, the channel is available to all site visitors, regardless of location."
msgstr ""
"Hvis denne kanal **kun** skal være tilgængelig for besøgende på webstedet i "
"bestemte lande, skal du tilføje dem til feltet :guilabel:`Land`. Hvis dette "
"felt efterlades tomt, er kanalen tilgængelig for alle besøgende på "
"webstedet, uanset placering."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:219
msgid ""
"In order to track the geographical location of visitors, *GeoIP* **must** be "
"installed on the database. While this feature is installed by default on "
"*Odoo Online* databases, *On-Premise* databases require "
"additional :doc:`setup steps </administration/on_premise/geo_ip>`."
msgstr ""
"For at spore den geografiske placering af besøgende **skal** *GeoIP* være "
"installeret på databasen. Selvom denne funktion er installeret som standard "
"på *Odoo Online*-databaser, kræver *On-Premise*-databaser yderligere "
":doc:`opsætningstrin </administration/on_premise/geo_ip>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:226
msgid "Widget tab"
msgstr "Fanen Widget"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:228
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Widget` tab on the live chat channel detail form provides an "
"embeddable code snippet for external, non-Odoo websites. This code can be "
"added to a website to provide access to a live chat window."
msgstr ""
"Fanen :guilabel:`Widget` på detaljeformularen for live chat-kanalen "
"indeholder et integrerbart kodestykke til eksterne, ikke-Odoo-websteder. "
"Denne kode kan tilføjes til et websted for at give adgang til et live chat-"
"vindue."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:233
msgid ""
"The live chat widget can be added to websites created through Odoo by "
"navigating to :menuselection:`Website app --> Configuration --> Settings`. "
"Then, scroll to the :menuselection:`Email & Marketing` section. In "
"the :guilabel:`Channel` field, select the channel to add to the site. "
"Click :guilabel:`Save` to apply."
msgstr ""
"Live chat-widgetten kan tilføjes til websteder oprettet via Odoo ved at "
"navigere til :menuselection:`Hjemmeside-app --> Konfiguration --> "
"Indstillinger`. Rul derefter til sektionen :menuselection:`E-mail og "
"marketing`. I feltet :guilabel:`Kanal` skal du vælge den kanal, der skal "
"tilføjes til siden. Klik på :guilabel:`Gem` for at anvende."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:238
msgid ""
"To add the widget to a website created on a third-party platform, click the "
"first :icon:`fa-clipboard` :guilabel:`(copy)` icon on the :guilabel:`Widget` "
"tab, and paste the code into the `<head>` tag on the site."
msgstr ""
"For at tilføje widgetten til et websted oprettet på en tredjepartsplatform "
"skal du klikke på det første :icon:`fa-clipboard` :guilabel:`(kopiér)`-ikon "
"på fanen :guilabel:`Widget` og indsætte koden i `<head>`-tagget på siden."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:242
msgid ""
"Likewise, to send a live chat session to a customer, click the "
"second :icon:`fa-clipboard` :guilabel:`(copy)` icon on "
"the :guilabel:`Widget` tab. This link can be sent directly to a customer. "
"When they click the link, they are redirected to a new chat window."
msgstr ""
"Ligeledes skal du klikke på det andet :icon:`fa-clipboard` :guilabel:`"
"(kopiér)`-ikon på fanen :guilabel:`Widget` for at sende en live chat-session "
"til en kunde. Dette link kan sendes direkte til en kunde. Når de klikker på "
"linket, omdirigeres de til et nyt chatvindue."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:None
msgid "View of the widget tab for Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr "Visning af widget-fanen for Odoo Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:250
msgid ":doc:`../productivity/discuss`"
msgstr ":doc:`../productivity/discuss`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:251
msgid ":doc:`livechat/responses`"
msgstr ":doc:`livechat/responses`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:252
msgid ":doc:`livechat/ratings`"
msgstr ":doc:`livechat/ratings`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:253
msgid ":doc:`livechat/chatbots`"
msgstr ":doc:`livechat/chatbots`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:254
msgid ":doc:`livechat/participate`"
msgstr ":doc:`livechat/participate`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:3
msgid "Chatbots"
msgstr "Chatbots"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:5
msgid ""
"A *Chatbot* is a program designed to mimic a conversation with a live human. "
"Chatbots are assigned a script of pre-written steps to follow. The scripts "
"are designed to anticipate a visitor's potential response, and lead them "
"through a series of questions and answers the same way a live team member "
"would."
msgstr ""
"*Chatbot* je program navržený tak, aby napodoboval konverzaci se živým "
"člověkem. Chatbotům je přiřazen skript s předem napsanými kroky, které mají "
"následovat. Skripty jsou navrženy tak, aby předvídaly potenciální odpověď "
"návštěvníka a vedly jej řadou otázek a odpovědí stejným způsobem, jakým by "
"to udělal živý člen týmu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:10
msgid ""
"Chatbots can be customized to fill various roles, from customer support, to "
"creating leads, to collecting contact information. The goal of each chatbot "
"can vary based on several criteria, including the webpage where it is "
"located, and the information it captures."
msgstr ""
"Chatboty lze přizpůsobit tak, aby plnily různé úlohy, od zákaznické podpory "
"přes vytváření leadů až po sběr kontaktních informací. Cíl každého chatbota "
"se může lišit na základě několika kritérií, včetně webové stránky, na které "
"se nachází, a informací, které zachycuje."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:0
msgid ""
"View of the chat window with a helpdesk ticket created in Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr ""
"Zobrazení okna chatu s vytvořeným ticketem pro kundeservice v Odoo Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:18
msgid "Build a chatbot"
msgstr "Vytvořit chatbota"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:20
msgid ""
"Before creating a new chatbot, the **Live Chat** application must first "
"be :ref:`installed <general/install>`."
msgstr ""
"Před vytvořením nového chatbota musí být nejprve :ref:`nainstalována "
"<general/install>` aplikace **Live Chat**."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:23
msgid ""
"After the **Live Chat** application has been installed on the database, go "
"to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Configuration --> Chatbots`."
msgstr ""
"Po instalaci aplikace **Live Chat** do databáze přejděte na "
":menuselection:`Live Chat --> Konfigurace --> Chatboti`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:27
msgid ""
"When the **Live Chat** app is installed, a sample chatbot is created, named "
"*Welcome Bot*. This chatbot has a preconfigured script that walks through a "
"few basic steps, including asking for a visitor's email address, and "
"forwarding the conversation to an operator."
msgstr ""
"Při instalaci aplikace **Live Chat** se vytvoří ukázkový chatbot s názvem "
"*Welcome Bot*. Tento chatbot má předkonfigurovaný skript, který prochází "
"několika základními kroky, včetně dotazu na e-mailovou adresu návštěvníka a "
"přesměrování konverzace na operátora."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:31
msgid ""
"*Welcome Bot* can be used as a starting point. The existing steps can be "
"edited or removed, and new steps can be added to customize the script, as "
"needed."
msgstr ""
"*Welcome Bot* lze použít jako výchozí bod. Existující kroky lze upravit nebo "
"odstranit a pro přizpůsobení skriptu lze přidat nové kroky podle potřeby."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:34
msgid "*Welcome Bot* can be deleted or archived, if necessary."
msgstr "V případě potřeby lze *Welcome Bot* smazat nebo archivovat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:0
msgid "View of the Welcome Bot script in Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr "Zobrazení skriptu Welcome Bot v Odoo Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:39
msgid ""
"To create a new chatbot, navigate to the :guilabel:`Chatbot` page "
"(:menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Configuration --> Chatbots`) and "
"click :guilabel:`New` to open a blank chatbot details page."
msgstr ""
"Chcete-li vytvořit nového chatbota, přejděte na stránku :guilabel:`Chatbot` "
"(:menuselection:`Live Chat --> Konfigurace --> Chatboti`) a klikněte na "
":guilabel:`Nový`. Otevře se prázdná stránka s podrobnostmi chatbota."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:42
msgid ""
"Enter a name in the :guilabel:`Chatbot Name` field and hover over the image "
"on the right. Click on the :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(pencil)` icon that "
"appears to add a photo."
msgstr ""
"Zadejte název do pole :guilabel:`Název chatbota` a najeďte myší na obrázek "
"vpravo. Klikněte na ikonu :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(tužka)`, která se "
"zobrazí, a přidejte fotografii."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:46
msgid "Chatbot scripts"
msgstr "Skripty chatbota"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:48
msgid ""
"After the new chatbot has been created and named, the next step is to create "
"a script. Chatbot conversations follow an accompanying script, comprised of "
"lines of dialog. Each line is designed to either deliver or capture "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Po vytvoření a pojmenování nového chatbota je dalším krokem vytvoření "
"skriptu. Konverzace chatbota se řídí doprovodným skriptem složeným z řádků "
"dialogu. Každý řádek je navržen tak, aby buď poskytoval, nebo zachycoval "
"informace."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:52
msgid ""
"To create a chatbot script, click :guilabel:`Add a Line` in "
"the :guilabel:`Script` tab of the chatbot detail page, and "
"a :guilabel:`Create Script Steps` pop-up window appears. This form must be "
"filled out for each line of text (dialog) that the chatbot could potentially "
"deliver during the conversation."
msgstr ""
"Pro vytvoření skriptu chatbota klikněte na :guilabel:`Přidat řádek` na kartě "
":guilabel:`Skript` na stránce s podrobnostmi chatbota a zobrazí se "
"vyskakovací okno :guilabel:`Vytvořit kroky skriptu`. Tento formulář musí být "
"vyplněn pro každý řádek textu (dialogu), který by chatbot mohl potenciálně "
"doručit během konverzace."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:57
msgid ""
"First, enter the content of the message in the :guilabel:`Message` field. "
"Then, select an option from the :guilabel:`Step Type` and :ref:`Only If "
"<livechat/chatbots/only-if>` drop-down menus."
msgstr ""
"Nejprve zadejte obsah zprávy do pole :guilabel:`Zpráva`. Poté vyberte "
"možnost z rozbalovacích nabídek :guilabel:`Typ kroku` a :ref:`Pouze pokud "
"<livechat/chatbots/only-if>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:61
msgid "Step types"
msgstr "Typy kroků"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:63
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Step Type` selected depends on the intended purpose of the "
"message. The available options in the :guilabel:`Step Type` drop-down menu "
"are detailed below."
msgstr ""
"Den valgte :guilabel:`trin type` afhænger af den tilsigtede hensigt med "
"beskeden. De tilgængelige muligheder i rullemenuen :guilabel:`Trin Type` er "
"beskrevet nedenfor."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:67
msgid "Text"
msgstr "Tekst"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:69
msgid ""
"This step is used for messages where no answer is expected or necessary. "
"Text steps can be used for greetings, to offer resources, such as "
"documentation, or provide links to specific web pages."
msgstr ""
"Dette trin bruges til beskeder, hvor der ikke forventes eller er brug for et "
"svar. Teksttrin kan bruges til hilsner, til at tilbyde ressourcer såsom "
"dokumentation eller give links til specifikke websider."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:73
msgid ""
"*Text* step types are only intended to deliver information, and do not allow "
"for any visitor input. As such, they must be followed by additional steps to "
"continue the conversation."
msgstr ""
"Trintyperne *tekst* er kun beregnet til at levere information og tillader "
"ikke input fra besøgende. Derfor skal de følges af yderligere trin for at "
"fortsætte samtalen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:77
msgid "Question"
msgstr "Spørgsmål"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:79
msgid ""
"This step asks a question and provides a set of answers. The visitor clicks "
"on one answer, which either leads to a new step in the conversation, or can "
"lead to an optional link to a new webpage."
msgstr ""
"Dette trin stiller et spørgsmål og tilbyder et sæt svar. Den besøgende "
"klikker på ét svar, som enten fører til et nyt trin i samtalen eller kan "
"føre til et valgfrit link til en ny webside."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:82
msgid ""
"Enter the question in the :guilabel:`Message` field. Then, under "
"the :guilabel:`Answer` heading, click :guilabel:`Add a Line` to create a "
"blank answer line."
msgstr ""
"Indtast spørgsmålet i feltet :guilabel:`Besked`. Klik derefter under "
"overskriften :guilabel:`Svar` på :guilabel:`Tilføj en linje` for at oprette "
"en tom svarlinje."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:85
msgid ""
"Proceed to enter the answer as it should appear to the visitor. To turn the "
"answer into a link that redirects the visitor when selected, add the URL to "
"the answer line under the :guilabel:`Optional Link` heading."
msgstr ""
"Indtast svaret, som det skal vises for den besøgende. For at gøre svaret til "
"et link, der omdirigerer den besøgende, når det vælges, skal du tilføje "
"URL'en til svarlinjen under overskriften :guilabel:`Valgfrit Link`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:89
msgid ""
"Repeat these steps for every answer to be included for the question. "
"Click :guilabel:`Save & Close` or :guilabel:`Save & New` when finished."
msgstr ""
"Gentag disse trin for hvert svar, der skal inkluderes i spørgsmålet. Klik på "
":guilabel:`Gem & Luk` eller :guilabel:`Gem & Ny`, når du er færdig."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:93
msgid ""
"It is helpful to add a catchall answer to question steps (e.g: `Something "
"else`). This helps visitors continue the conversation, even if their needs "
"do not fit with any of the other answers."
msgstr ""
"Det er nyttigt at tilføje et opsamlingssvar til spørgsmålstrin (f.eks.: "
"`Noget andet`). Dette hjælper besøgende med at fortsætte samtalen, selv hvis "
"deres behov ikke passer med nogen af de andre svar."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:97
msgid "Email"
msgstr "E-mail"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:99
msgid ""
"This step prompts visitors to provide their email address, which is stored "
"and can be used by team members later to follow up with additional "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Dette trin beder besøgende om at angive deres e-mailadresse, som gemmes og "
"kan bruges af teammedlemmer senere til at følge op med yderligere "
"information."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:102
msgid ""
"The only accepted inputs for this step type are email addresses that are in "
"a valid format. If a visitor attempts to enter anything other than a valid "
"email address, the chatbot responds with a message stating it does not "
"recognize the information submitted."
msgstr ""
"De eneste accepterede input til denne trintype er e-mailadresser i et "
"gyldigt format. Hvis en besøgende forsøger at indtaste andet end en gyldig e-"
"mailadresse, svarer chatbotten med en besked om, at den ikke genkender de "
"indsendte oplysninger."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:None
msgid "View of a chatbot responding to an invalid email."
msgstr "Visning af en chatbot, der reagerer på en ugyldig e-mail."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:110
msgid "Phone"
msgstr "Telefon"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:112
msgid ""
"Similar to email, this step type prompts the visitor to enter their phone "
"number, which can be used to follow up with additional information, schedule "
"demos, and more."
msgstr ""
"I lighed med e-mail beder denne trintype den besøgende om at indtaste deres "
"telefonnummer, som kan bruges til at følge op med yderligere information, "
"planlægge demoer og meget mere."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:116
msgid ""
"Due to the vast number of formats used for phone numbers worldwide, "
"responses to this step type are not validated for formatting, and can "
"include both numbers and special characters."
msgstr ""
"På grund af det store antal formater, der bruges til telefonnumre over hele "
"verden, valideres svar på denne trintype ikke for formatering og kan omfatte "
"både tal og specialtegn."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:120
msgid "Forward to Operator"
msgstr "Videresend til operatør"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:122
msgid ""
"This step forwards the conversation to an active live chat operator, so they "
"can continue assisting the visitor. As the conversation transcript is passed "
"on to the operator, they can pick up where the chatbot left off. This not "
"only saves time for all parties involved, it can also help qualify "
"conversations before they reach live operators."
msgstr ""
"Dette trin videresender samtalen til en aktiv live chat-operatør, så de kan "
"fortsætte med at hjælpe den besøgende. Da samtaleudskriften overføres til "
"operatøren, kan de fortsætte, hvor chatbotten slap. Dette sparer ikke kun "
"tid for alle involverede parter, det kan også hjælpe med at kvalificere "
"samtaler, før de når live-operatører."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:128
msgid ""
"If no active operator is available on the channel, the chatbot continues the "
"conversation with the visitor. Therefore, additional steps should be added "
"after this one to ensure there is no abrupt end to the conversation. The "
"additional steps can both inform visitors about the lack of available "
"operators (e.g. `Uh-oh, it looks like none of our operators are available`) "
"and continue the conversation (e.g. `Would you like to leave your email "
"address?`)."
msgstr ""
"Hvis ingen aktiv operatør er tilgængelig på kanalen, fortsætter chatbotten "
"samtalen med den besøgende. Derfor bør der tilføjes yderligere trin efter "
"dette for at sikre, at der ikke er en brat afslutning på samtalen. De "
"yderligere trin kan både informere besøgende om manglen på tilgængelige "
"operatører (f.eks. `Hovsa, det ser ud til, at ingen af vores operatører er "
"tilgængelige`) og fortsætte samtalen (f.eks. `Vil du gerne efterlade din e-"
"mailadresse?`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:0
msgid ""
"View of a chatbot follow up messages when no live chat operator is available."
msgstr ""
"Visning af en chatbots opfølgende beskeder, når ingen live chat-operatør er "
"tilgængelig."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:138
msgid "Free Input/Multi-Line"
msgstr "Fri indtastning/flere linjer"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:140
msgid ""
"The *free input* step allows visitors to respond to questions without "
"providing pre-written responses. Information provided in these responses is "
"stored in the chat transcripts."
msgstr ""
"Trinnet *fri indtastning* giver besøgende mulighed for at svare på spørgsmål "
"uden at levere forudskrevne svar. Information, der gives i disse svar, "
"gemmes i chatudskrifterne."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:143
msgid ""
"Choose between :guilabel:`Free Input` and :guilabel:`Free Input (Multi-"
"Line)` depending on the type and amount of information the visitor is asked "
"to provide."
msgstr ""
"Vælg mellem :guilabel:`Fri Indtastning` og :guilabel:`Fri Indtastning (Flere "
"Linjer)` afhængigt af typen og mængden af information, som den besøgende "
"bliver bedt om at give."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:147
msgid "Create Lead"
msgstr "Opret kundeemne"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:149
msgid ""
"This step creates a lead in the **CRM** application. Select an option from "
"the :guilabel:`Sales Team` drop-down field that appears to assign the "
"created lead to a specific team."
msgstr ""
"Dette trin opretter et lead i **CRM**-applikationen. Vælg en mulighed fra "
"rullemenuen :guilabel:`Salgsteam`, der vises, for at tildele det oprettede "
"lead til et specifikt team."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:153
msgid ""
"This step is only available if the **CRM** application is installed on the "
"database."
msgstr ""
"Tento krok je dostupný pouze v případě, že je v databázi nainstalována "
"aplikace **CRM**."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:156
msgid "Create Ticket"
msgstr "Opret supportbillet"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:158
msgid ""
"This step creates a :doc:`ticket <../../services/helpdesk/overview/"
"receiving_tickets>` in the **Helpdesk** application. Select an option from "
"the :guilabel:`Helpdesk Team` drop-down field that appears to assign the "
"created ticket to a specific team."
msgstr ""
"Tento krok vytvoří :doc:`tiket <../../services/helpdesk/overview/"
"receiving_tickets>` v aplikaci **Kundeservice**. Vyberte možnost z "
"rozbalovacího pole :guilabel:`Helpdesk Team`, které se zobrazí, a přiřaďte "
"vytvořený tiket konkrétnímu týmu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:163
msgid ""
"This step is only available if the **Helpdesk** application is installed on "
"the database."
msgstr ""
"Tento krok je dostupný pouze v případě, že je v databázi nainstalována "
"aplikace **Kundeservice**."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:168
msgid "Only if"
msgstr "Pouze pokud"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:170
msgid ""
"Chatbot scripts operate on an if/then basis, which means the next question "
"presented to the visitor is determined by the answer provided to the "
"previous question."
msgstr ""
"Chatbot skripty fungují na principu pokud/pak, což znamená, že následující "
"otázka předložená návštěvníkovi je určena odpovědí na předchozí otázku."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:173
msgid ""
"To continue the progression of the conversation, the :guilabel:`Create "
"Script Steps` form for a new step contains a field labeled :guilabel:`Only "
"If`. This field is where the progression of questions are defined."
msgstr ""
"Pro pokračování konverzace obsahuje formulář :guilabel:`Create Script Steps` "
"pro nový krok pole označené :guilabel:`Pouze pokud`. V tomto poli se "
"definuje průběh otázek."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:177
msgid ""
"If a step is intended to follow all of the previous messages, this field can "
"be left empty. However, if a message should only be sent conditionally, "
"based on a previous response, or several previous responses, those responses "
"**must** be added to this field."
msgstr ""
"Pokud má krok následovat po všech předchozích zprávách, může toto pole "
"zůstat prázdné. Pokud však má být zpráva odeslána pouze podmíněně, na "
"základě předchozí odpovědi nebo několika předchozích odpovědí, tyto odpovědi "
"**musí** být do tohoto pole přidány."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:182
msgid ""
"If any selections are made in the :guilabel:`Only If` field, they must all "
"be selected during the conversation before this step is included. Only "
"include selections in this field if they are necessary for this step to be "
"displayed."
msgstr ""
"Pokud jsou v poli :guilabel:`Pouze pokud` provedeny jakékoli výběry, musí "
"být všechny vybrány během konverzace, než bude tento krok zahrnut. Do tohoto "
"pole zahrnujte pouze výběry, které jsou nezbytné k zobrazení tohoto kroku."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:187
msgid ""
"In the *Welcome Bot* script, a visitor can ask about pricing information. If "
"the visitor selects this response, a step is included to forward the "
"conversation to an operator. The chatbot first sends a message informing the "
"visitor that it is checking to see if an operator is available to assist "
"with pricing information."
msgstr ""
"Ve skriptu *Welcome Bot* se návštěvník může zeptat na informace o cenách. "
"Pokud návštěvník vybere tuto odpověď, je zahrnut krok pro předání konverzace "
"operátorovi. Chatbot nejprve odešle zprávu informující návštěvníka, že "
"kontroluje, zda je k dispozici operátor, který pomůže s informacemi o cenách."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:192
msgid ""
"However, this message should only be delivered if the visitor requests "
"pricing information. In that situation, the conversation would proceed as "
"below:"
msgstr ""
"Tato zpráva by však měla být doručena pouze v případě, že návštěvník požádá "
"o informace o cenách. V této situaci by konverzace probíhala následovně:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:195
msgid "Welcome Bot: \"*What are you looking for?*\""
msgstr "Welcome Bot: \"*Co hledáte?*\""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:196
msgid "Visitor: \"**I have a pricing question.**\""
msgstr "Návštěvník: \"**Mám otázku ohledně cen.**\""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:197
msgid ""
"Welcome Bot: \"*Hmmm, let me check if I can find someone that could help you "
"with that...*\""
msgstr ""
"Welcome Bot: \"*Hmmm, nechte mě zkontrolovat, jestli najdu někoho, kdo by "
"vám s tím mohl pomoci...*\""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:199
msgid ""
"In the details form for the :guilabel:`Text` step, the *I have a pricing "
"question* response has been selected in the :guilabel:`Only If` field. As "
"such, this step is only shown in conversations where that response has been "
"selected."
msgstr ""
"Ve formuláři podrobností pro krok :guilabel:`Text` byla v poli "
":guilabel:`Pouze pokud` vybrána odpověď *Mám otázku ohledně cen*. Proto je "
"tento krok zobrazen pouze v konverzacích, kde byla tato odpověď vybrána."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:0
msgid "View of the new message form emphasizing the Only If field."
msgstr "Zobrazení formuláře nové zprávy se zvýrazněním pole Pouze pokud."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:207
msgid "Script testing"
msgstr "Testování skriptu"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:209
msgid ""
"To ensure all visitors have a satisfactory experience with the chatbot, each "
"message needs to lead to a natural conclusion. Chatbot scripts should be "
"tested to confirm there are no dead-ends, and to understand what the visitor "
"sees when they interact with the chatbot."
msgstr ""
"Aby všichni návštěvníci měli uspokojivou zkušenost s chatbotem, musí každá "
"zpráva vést k přirozenému závěru. Chatbot skripty by měly být testovány, aby "
"bylo potvrzeno, že neexistují slepé uličky, a aby bylo možné pochopit, co "
"návštěvník vidí při interakci s chatbotem."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:214
msgid ""
"If the visitor provides an answer, or input, that is not assigned a "
"corresponding follow-up response, the conversation stops (*dead-ends*). "
"Since the visitor cannot re-engage the chatbot, they must restart the "
"conversation by refreshing the chat window, or their browser. They may also "
"click on the :icon:`fa-refresh` :guilabel:`(refresh)` icon at the top of the "
"message window."
msgstr ""
"Pokud návštěvník poskytne odpověď nebo vstup, ke kterému není přiřazena "
"odpovídající následná odpověď, konverzace se zastaví (*slepá ulička*). "
"Protože návštěvník nemůže chatbota znovu aktivovat, musí konverzaci "
"restartovat obnovením okna chatu nebo prohlížeče. Může také kliknout na "
"ikonu :icon:`fa-refresh` :guilabel:`(obnovit)` v horní části okna zpráv."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:0
msgid "The refresh button at the top of the message window."
msgstr "Tlačítko obnovení v horní části okna zpráv."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:222
msgid ""
"The :icon:`fa-refresh` (refresh) icon only appears when the chatbot script "
"has reached a dead-end."
msgstr ""
"Ikona :icon:`fa-refresh` (obnovit) se zobrazí pouze v případě, že chatbot "
"skript dosáhl slepé uličky."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:225
msgid ""
"To test the performance of a chatbot, first click on the :guilabel:`Test` "
"button at the top-left of the chatbot script page. Then, upon being "
"redirected to the testing screen, answer the chatbot prompts the same way a "
"potential site visitor would."
msgstr ""
"For at teste en chatbots ydeevne skal du først klikke på knappen "
":guilabel:`Test` øverst til venstre på chatbot-scriptsiden. Når du derefter "
"bliver omdirigeret til testskærmen, skal du besvare chatbot-promptsne på "
"samme måde, som en potentiel besøgende på websitet ville gøre."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:229
msgid ""
"When the script has reached an end-point, the message *Conversation "
"ended...* appears at the bottom of the chat window. To begin the "
"conversation at the beginning of the script, click on the :icon:`fa-"
"refresh` :guilabel:`(refresh)` icon at the top of the message window. To "
"return to the script page, click :guilabel:`Back to edit mode` at the top of "
"the page."
msgstr ""
"Når scriptet har nået et slutpunkt, vises meddelelsen *Conversation "
"ended...* nederst i chatvinduet. For at begynde samtalen fra begyndelsen af "
"scriptet skal du klikke på ikonet :icon:`fa-refresh` :guilabel:`opdater` "
"øverst i meddelelsesvinduet. For at vende tilbage til scriptsiden skal du "
"klikke på :guilabel:`Tilbage til redigeringstilstand` øverst på siden."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:235
msgid "Add chatbot to a channel"
msgstr "Tilføj chatbot til en kanal"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:237
msgid ""
"After a chatbot has been created and tested, it needs to be added to a live "
"chat channel."
msgstr ""
"Når en chatbot er blevet oprettet og testet, skal den tilføjes til en live "
"chat-kanal."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:239
msgid ""
"First, open the :menuselection:`Live Chat` application, find the Kanban card "
"for the appropriate live chat channel, hover over it, and click "
"the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` icon to open the "
"drop-down menu. Click :guilabel:`Configure Channel` to open the channel "
"detail form."
msgstr ""
"Åbn først applikationen :menuselection:`Live Chat`, find Kanban-kortet for "
"den relevante live chat-kanal, hold musen over det og klik på ikonet "
":icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`lodret ellipse` for at åbne rullemenuen. "
"Klik på :guilabel:`Konfigurer kanal` for at åbne kanaldetaljeskemaet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:245
msgid ""
"To create a new live chat channel, open the :menuselection:`Live Chat app` "
"and click :guilabel:`New`. See :doc:`Live Chat <../livechat>` for more "
"information."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette en ny live chat-kanal skal du åbne :menuselection:`Live Chat-"
"appen` og klikke på :guilabel:`Ny`. Se :doc:`Live Chat <../livechat>` for "
"mere information."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:248
msgid ""
"Click on the :guilabel:`Channel Rules` tab. Then, open an existing rule, or "
"create a new one by clicking :guilabel:`Add a line`."
msgstr ""
"Klik på fanen :guilabel:`Kanalregler`. Åbn derefter en eksisterende regel "
"eller opret en ny ved at klikke på :guilabel:`Tilføj en linje`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:251
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Create Rules` pop-up window, choose the appropriate "
"chatbot in the :guilabel:`Chatbot` field."
msgstr ""
"I pop op-vinduet :guilabel:`Opret regler` skal du vælge den relevante "
"chatbot i feltet :guilabel:`Chatbot`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:254
msgid ""
"If the chatbot should only be active if there are no live chat operators "
"available, check the box labeled :guilabel:`Enabled only if no operator`."
msgstr ""
"Hvis chatbotten kun skal være aktiv, når der ikke er nogen live chat-"
"operatører tilgængelige, skal du markere boksen mærket :guilabel:`Kun "
"aktiveret hvis ingen operatør`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:None
msgid "View of the channel rules emphasizing the chatbot field."
msgstr "Visning af kanalreglerne med fremhævelse af chatbot-feltet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:261
msgid ":doc:`Live chat channel rules </applications/websites/livechat>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Regler for live chat-kanal </applications/websites/livechat>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:3
msgid "Participate in live chat"
msgstr "Deltag i live chat"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:5
msgid ""
"*Operators* are the users who respond to live chat requests from customers "
"and website visitors. The information below outlines the necessary steps for "
"operators participating in live chat conversations on an Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"*Operatører* er de brugere, der reagerer på live chat-anmodninger fra kunder "
"og besøgende på websitet. Informationen nedenfor beskriver de nødvendige "
"trin for operatører, der deltager i live chat-samtaler på en Odoo-database."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:10
msgid "Set an online chat name"
msgstr "Indstil et online chatnavn"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:12
msgid ""
"Before participating in a live chat, operators may choose to update their "
"*Online Chat Name*. This is the name displayed to site visitors in the live "
"chat conversation."
msgstr ""
"Før deltagelse i en live chat kan operatører vælge at opdatere deres *Online "
"chatnavn*. Dette er det navn, der vises for besøgende på websitet i live "
"chat-samtalen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:15
msgid ""
"To update the *Online Chat Name*, click on the user avatar in the top-right "
"corner of any page in the database. Select :guilabel:`My Profile` from the "
"drop-down menu to open the profile page. On the right side of "
"the :guilabel:`Preferences` tab, locate the :guilabel:`Online Chat Name` "
"field, and enter a preferred name."
msgstr ""
"For at opdatere *Online chatnavnet* skal du klikke på brugeravataren øverst "
"til højre på enhver side i databasen. Vælg :guilabel:`Min profil` fra "
"rullemenuen for at åbne profilsiden. På højre side af fanen "
":guilabel:`Præferencer` skal du finde feltet :guilabel:`Online chatnavn` og "
"indtaste et foretrukket navn."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:20
msgid ""
"If a user's :guilabel:`Online Chat Name` is not set, the name displayed "
"defaults to the user's name that is designated on their profile page."
msgstr ""
"Hvis en brugers :guilabel:`Online chatnavn` ikke er angivet, vises som "
"standard brugerens navn, der er angivet på deres profilside."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:24
msgid ""
"Mitchell Admin has his full name as his :guilabel:`User Name`, but he does "
"not want to include his last name in a live chat conversation for privacy "
"reasons. He would then set his :guilabel:`Online Chat Name` to include only "
"his first name, Mitchell."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:0
msgid "View of user profile in Odoo, emphasizing the Online Chat name field."
msgstr ""
"Visning af brugerprofil i Odoo med fremhævelse af feltet Online chatnavn."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:32
msgid "Set online chat languages"
msgstr "Indstil online chatsprog"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:34
msgid ""
"If an operator speaks multiple languages, they can add this information to "
"their user profile. This information can then be used to determine which "
"conversations the operator is assigned. A visitor's language is determined "
"via their browser's language settings."
msgstr ""
"Hvis en operatør taler flere sprog, kan de tilføje disse oplysninger til "
"deres brugerprofil. Disse oplysninger kan derefter bruges til at bestemme, "
"hvilke samtaler operatøren bliver tildelt. En besøgendes sprog bestemmes via "
"deres browsers sprogindstillinger."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:39
msgid ""
"Conversations are assigned to operators based on a number of criteria, "
"including availability and the number of ongoing conversations. While the "
"operator's main language and additional languages are taken into "
"consideration, they do **not** supersede all other criteria."
msgstr ""
"Samtaler tildeles operatører baseret på en række kriterier, herunder "
"tilgængelighed og antallet af igangværende samtaler. Selvom operatørens "
"hovedsprog og yderligere sprog tages i betragtning, tilsidesætter de "
"**ikke** alle andre kriterier."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:43
msgid ""
"To add *Online Chat Languages*, click on the user avatar in the top-right "
"corner of any page in the database. Select :guilabel:`My Profile` from the "
"drop-down menu to open the profile page. On the right side of "
"the :guilabel:`Preferences` tab, click into the :guilabel:`Online Chat "
"Language` field, and select one or more languages from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"For at tilføje *Online chatsproget* skal du klikke på brugeravataren i "
"øverste højre hjørne af en hvilken som helst side i databasen. Vælg "
":guilabel:`Min profil` fra rullemenuen for at åbne profilsiden. På højre "
"side af fanen :guilabel:`Præferencer` skal du klikke i feltet "
":guilabel:`Online chatsprog` og vælge et eller flere sprog fra rullemenuen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:49
msgid ""
"Only :doc:`languages <../../general/users/language>` that are enabled on the "
"database can be selected in the :guilabel:`Online Chat Language` field."
msgstr ""
"Kun :doc:`sprog <../../general/users/language>`, der er aktiveret i "
"databasen, kan vælges i feltet :guilabel:`Online chatsprog`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:53
msgid "Join or leave a channel"
msgstr "Tilslutte eller forlade en kanal"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:55
msgid ""
"To join a live chat channel, go to the :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> "
"Channels`, and click the :guilabel:`Join` button on the Kanban card for the "
"appropriate channel."
msgstr ""
"For at tilslutte en live chat-kanal skal du gå til :menuselection:`Live Chat-"
"app --> Kanaler` og klikke på knappen :guilabel:`Tilslut` på Kanban-kortet "
"for den relevante kanal."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:58
msgid ""
"Any channel where the user is currently active shows a :guilabel:`Leave` "
"button. Click this button to disconnect from the channel."
msgstr ""
"Enhver kanal, hvor brugeren i øjeblikket er aktiv, viser en "
":guilabel:`Forlad`-knap. Klik på denne knap for at afbryde forbindelsen til "
"kanalen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of a channel form and the option to join a channel for Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr ""
"Visning af en kanalformular og muligheden for at tilslutte en kanal til Odoo "
"Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:65
msgid ""
"Operators that do not show any activity in Odoo for more than thirty minutes "
"are considered disconnected, and subsequently removed from the channel."
msgstr ""
"Operatører, der ikke viser nogen aktivitet i Odoo i mere end tredive "
"minutter, betragtes som afbrudt og fjernes efterfølgende fra kanalen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:69
msgid "Manage live chat requests"
msgstr "Administrere live chat-anmodninger"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:71
msgid ""
"When an operator is active in a channel, chat windows open in the bottom-"
"right corner of the screen, no matter what page they are on in Odoo. This "
"allows them to access other pages and apps, while still participating in the "
"conversation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:75
msgid ""
"Live chat conversations can also be viewed by navigating to "
"the :menuselection:`Discuss app`. New conversations appear in bold under the "
"channel name, located along the left panel."
msgstr ""
"Live chat-samtaler kan også ses ved at navigere til :menuselection:`Beskeder-"
"app`. Nye samtaler vises med fed skrift under kanalnavnet, som er placeret i "
"venstre panel."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of the discuss application with a message sent through live chat in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Visning af Beskeder-applikationen med en besked sendt via live chat i Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:81
msgid ""
"Click on a conversation in the left panel to open it. From this view, an "
"operator can participate in the chat the same as they would in the normal "
"chat window."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:85
msgid ""
"Conversations can also be accessed by clicking the :icon:`fa-"
"comments` :guilabel:`(messages)` icon in the menu bar."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:0
msgid "View of the menu bar in Odoo emphasizing the comments icon."
msgstr "Visning af menulinjen i Odoo med fremhævelse af kommentarikonet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:92
msgid ":doc:`../../productivity/discuss`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../productivity/discuss`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:93
msgid ":doc:`../livechat`"
msgstr ":doc:`../livechat`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:94
msgid ":doc:`../livechat/responses`"
msgstr ":doc:`../livechat/responses`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:3
msgid "Ratings"
msgstr "Bedømmelser"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:9
msgid ""
"At the end of a **Live Chat** conversation, customers have the opportunity "
"to rate the quality of support they received from the live chat *operator*. "
"Customers provide ratings as soon as they close the conversation. This "
"allows operators to receive immediate feedback on their performance. It also "
"allows customers to share any final comments before leaving the chat window."
msgstr ""
"Efter afslutningen af en **Live Chat**-samtale har kunder mulighed for at "
"vurdere kvaliteten af den support, de modtog fra *operatøren* i live "
"chatten. Kunder afgiver deres vurdering, så snart de lukker samtalen. Dette "
"gør det muligt for operatører at modtage øjeblikkelig feedback på deres "
"præstation. Det giver også kunderne mulighed for at dele eventuelle "
"afsluttende kommentarer, før de forlader chatvinduet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:15
msgid "Rate live chat conversations"
msgstr "Vurder live chat-samtaler"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:17
msgid ""
"Customers end a live chat conversation by clicking the :icon:`oi-"
"close` :guilabel:`(close)` icon in the upper right-hand corner of the chat "
"window. They are then prompted to select an icon that reflects their level "
"of satisfaction. The icons represent the following ratings:"
msgstr ""
"Kunder afslutter en live chat-samtale ved at klikke på :icon:`oi-close` "
":guilabel:`(luk)`-ikonet i øverste højre hjørne af chatvinduet. De bliver "
"derefter bedt om at vælge et ikon, der afspejler deres tilfredshedsniveau. "
"Ikonerne repræsenterer følgende vurderinger:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:21
msgid "**Satisfied** - |smile|"
msgstr "**Tilfreds** - |smile|"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:22
msgid "**Okay** - |meh|"
msgstr "**Okay** - |meh|"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:23
msgid "**Dissatisfied** - |frown|"
msgstr "**Utilfreds** - |frown|"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:None
msgid "View of the chat window from a user's side for Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr "Visning af chatvinduet fra en brugers side i Odoo Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:29
msgid ""
"When customers end a conversation, a field marked :guilabel:`Receive a copy "
"of this conversation` appears under the *ratings* icons. Customers can enter "
"their email either before or after they submit a rating."
msgstr ""
"Når kunder afslutter en samtale, vises et felt markeret :guilabel:`Modtag en "
"kopi af denne samtale` under *vurderings*-ikonerne. Kunder kan indtaste "
"deres e-mail enten før eller efter, de indsender en vurdering."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:33
msgid ""
"If the customer selects the |smile|, they are presented with a thank you "
"message and a :guilabel:`Close Conversation` link."
msgstr ""
"Hvis kunden vælger |smile|, præsenteres de for en takkebesked og et "
":guilabel:`Luk samtale`-link."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:None
msgid "View of customer's live chat window with thank you message."
msgstr "Visning af kundens live chat-vindue med takkebesked."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:39
msgid ""
"If the customer selects either the |meh| or the |frown|, a text box appears. "
"Customers can add comments in this text box to explain why they chose this "
"rating. This message, along with the rating icon, is sent to the live chat "
"operator."
msgstr ""
"Hvis kunden vælger enten |meh| eller |frown|, vises en tekstboks. Kunder kan "
"tilføje kommentarer i denne tekstboks for at forklare, hvorfor de valgte "
"denne vurdering. Denne besked sendes sammen med vurderingsikonet til live "
"chat-operatøren."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of a chat window from an operator's window highlighting a rating for "
"Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr ""
"Visning af et chatvindue fra en operatørs vindue, der fremhæver en vurdering "
"for Odoo Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:47
msgid "Publish customer ratings"
msgstr "Publicer kundevurderinger"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:49
msgid ""
"To publish a channel's ratings on the website, first navigate to a live chat "
"channel's record by going to the :menuselection:`Live Chat` app and clicking "
"on the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` icon on the "
"Kanban card for that team. Then, click :guilabel:`Configure Channel` to open "
"the channel details form. Then click on the :guilabel:`Go to Website` smart "
"button. This opens the :guilabel:`Live Chat Channel Statistics` page."
msgstr ""
"For at publicere en kanals vurderinger på hjemmesiden skal du først navigere "
"til en live chat-kanals post ved at gå til :menuselection:`Live Chat`-appen "
"og klikke på :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(lodret ellipse)`-ikonet på "
"Kanban-kortet for det pågældende team. Klik derefter på "
":guilabel:`Konfigurer kanal` for at åbne kanalens detaljeformular. Klik "
"derefter på :guilabel:`Gå til hjemmeside`-smart-knappen. Dette åbner siden "
":guilabel:`Live Chat-kanalstatistik`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:55
msgid ""
"In the upper right corner of the page, click the red :guilabel:`Unpublished` "
"slider. The slider changes from :guilabel:`Unpublished` "
"to :guilabel:`Published`."
msgstr ""
"I øverste højre hjørne af siden skal du klikke på den røde :guilabel:`Ikke "
"publiceret`-skyder. Skyderen ændres fra :guilabel:`Ikke publiceret` til "
":guilabel:`Publiceret`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:None
msgid "View of the published ratings on the portal for Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr "Visning af de publicerede vurderinger på portalen for Odoo Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:62
msgid ""
"The customer notes submitted with the rating are *not* published on the "
"website; they are kept internal. Only a statistical overview of the "
"operators' performance for the *channel* appears on the website."
msgstr ""
"De kundekommentarer, der indsendes sammen med vurderingen, bliver *ikke* "
"publiceret på hjemmesiden; de forbliver interne. Kun en statistisk oversigt "
"over operatørernes præstation for *kanalen* vises på hjemmesiden."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:67
msgid "Add ratings page to site"
msgstr "Tilføj bedømmelsesside til hjemmeside"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:69
msgid ""
"Once the rating page has been published, it has to be manually added to the "
"website. To do this, go to the main Odoo dashboard and open the **Website** "
"application. :menuselection:`Website app --> Site --> Pages`, then "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Når bedømmelsessiden er blevet publiceret, skal den manuelt tilføjes til "
"hjemmesiden. Gå til hovedoversigten i Odoo og åbn **Hjemmeside**-"
"applikationen. :menuselection:`Hjemmeside-app --> Websted --> Sider`, klik "
"derefter på :guilabel:`Ny`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:73
msgid ""
"This opens a :guilabel:`New Page` pop-up window. In the :guilabel:`Page "
"Title` field, enter `livechat`. This acts as the URL for the published "
"webpage."
msgstr ""
"Dette åbner et :guilabel:`Ny side`-pop op-vindue. I feltet "
":guilabel:`Sidetitel` skal du indtaste `livechat`. Dette fungerer som URL'en "
"for den publicerede webside."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:77
msgid ""
"The URL *must* be named `livechat` in order for the database to recognize "
"and connect the ratings page. After the page has been published, the page "
"title can be changed later under the :guilabel:`Menu Editor`."
msgstr ""
"URL'en *skal* hedde `livechat`, for at databasen kan genkende og forbinde "
"bedømmelsessiden. Efter at siden er blevet publiceret, kan sidetitlen ændres "
"senere under :guilabel:`Menuredigering`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:81
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Create`, and the newly created webpage opens. "
"The :guilabel:`Web Editor` appears in the right panel."
msgstr ""
"Klik på :guilabel:`Opret`, så åbnes den nyoprettede webside. "
":guilabel:`Webredigering` vises i højre panel."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:84
msgid ""
"The page lists the names of the :guilabel:`Live Chat Channels` whose ratings "
"pages have been published. On the left side of the channel name is an icon, "
"which users can click on to go to the ratings page for the respective "
"channel."
msgstr ""
"Siden viser navnene på de :guilabel:`Live Chat-kanaler`, hvis "
"bedømmelsessider er blevet publiceret. På venstre side af kanalnavnet er der "
"et ikon, som brugere kan klikke på for at gå til bedømmelsessiden for den "
"pågældende kanal."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:None
msgid "View of the webpage for Live Chat ratings emphasizing the channel icon."
msgstr ""
"Visning af websiden for Live Chat-bedømmelser med fremhævning af kanalikonen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:92
msgid ""
"The icon displayed on this page is configured on the live chat channel's "
"configuration page. To update this image, navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`Live Chat` app and click on the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-"
"v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` icon on the Kanban card for that team. "
"Then, click :guilabel:`Configure Channel` to open the channel details form. "
"Click the :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(pencil)` icon in the image box to "
"upload an image."
msgstr ""
"Ikonet, der vises på denne side, konfigureres på livechat-kanalens "
"konfigurationsside. For at opdatere dette billede skal du navigere til "
":menuselection:`Live Chat`-appen og klikke på :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` "
":guilabel:`(lodret ellipse)`-ikonet på Kanban-kortet for det pågældende "
"team. Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Konfigurer kanal` for at åbne "
"kanaldetaljernes formular. Klik på :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(blyant)`-"
"ikonet i billedboksen for at uploade et billede."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:98
msgid ""
"Make any desired changes or additions to this page, then "
"click :guilabel:`Save` in the top right of the webpage editor. The website "
"editor side panel closes, and the webpage remains on the screen."
msgstr ""
"Foretag eventuelle ønskede ændringer eller tilføjelser til denne side, klik "
"derefter på :guilabel:`Gem` i øverste højre hjørne af websideredigeringen. "
"Hjemmesideredigeringens sidepanel lukkes, og websiden forbliver på skærmen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:101
msgid ""
"To publish the `livechat` webpage, return to the list of webpages by "
"navigating to :menuselection:`Site --> Content --> Pages`. Click the "
"checkbox to the left of `livechat` in the list of pages to select the page "
"and highlight the line. Then, click the checkbox under the column "
"labeled :guilabel:`Is Published`. The field with the checkbox is highlighted "
"in white. Click the checkbox a second time to activate the :guilabel:`Is "
"Published` box. The webpage is now published."
msgstr ""
"For at publicere `livechat`-websiden skal du vende tilbage til listen over "
"websider ved at navigere til :menuselection:`Websted --> Indhold --> Sider`. "
"Klik på afkrydsningsfeltet til venstre for `livechat` på listen over sider "
"for at vælge siden og fremhæve linjen. Klik derefter på afkrydsningsfeltet "
"under kolonnen mærket :guilabel:`Er publiceret`. Feltet med "
"afkrydsningsfeltet fremhæves med hvidt. Klik på afkrydsningsfeltet en anden "
"gang for at aktivere :guilabel:`Er publiceret`-boksen. Websiden er nu "
"publiceret."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of the list of pages for a website with the 'is published' box "
"emphasized."
msgstr ""
"Visning af listen over sider for en hjemmeside med fremhævning af 'er "
"publiceret'-boksen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:110
msgid ""
"Once the page has been added to the site, ratings are set to be published by "
"default. However, individual ratings can be manually selected to be hidden "
"from the public. The rating is still included in internal reports, and can "
"still be viewed by internal teams. However, public website visitors and "
"portal users do not have access."
msgstr ""
"Når siden er blevet tilføjet til webstedet, er bedømmelser indstillet til at "
"blive publiceret som standard. Dog kan individuelle bedømmelser manuelt "
"vælges til at være skjult for offentligheden. Bedømmelsen er stadig "
"inkluderet i interne rapporter og kan stadig ses af interne teams. Dog har "
"offentlige hjemmesidebesøgende og portalbrugere ikke adgang."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:115
msgid ""
"See :ref:`Hide individual ratings <livechat/overview/hide-ratings>` for more "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Se :ref:`Skjul individuelle bedømmelser <livechat/overview/hide-ratings>` "
"for mere information."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:118
msgid "Customer ratings report"
msgstr "Kundebedømmelsesrapport"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:120
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Customer Ratings` report (:menuselection:`Live Chat --> "
"Report --> Customer Ratings`) displays an overview of the ratings received "
"on live chat conversations, as well as any additional comments submitted "
"with the rating."
msgstr ""
"Rapporten :guilabel:`Kundebedømmelser` (:menuselection:`Live Chat --> "
"Rapport --> Kundebedømmelser`) viser en oversigt over de bedømmelser, der er "
"modtaget i livechat-samtaler, samt eventuelle yderligere kommentarer, der er "
"indsendt sammen med bedømmelsen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:None
msgid "View of the customer ratings report in Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr "Visning af kundebedømmelsesrapporten i Odoo Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:127
msgid ""
"The report defaults to a Kanban view, with each rating represented by a "
"different card. To switch to a different view, click on one of the icons in "
"the upper-right corner of the screen. The report is available in *list* "
"view, *pivot* view, and *graph* view."
msgstr ""
"Rapporten vises som standard i Kanban-visning, hvor hver bedømmelse er "
"repræsenteret af et andet kort. For at skifte til en anden visning skal du "
"klikke på et af ikonerne i øverste højre hjørne af skærmen. Rapporten er "
"tilgængelig i *liste*-visning, *pivot*-visning og *graf*-visning."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:131
msgid ""
"Click on an individual rating to see additional details about the "
"conversation, and the rating."
msgstr ""
"Klik på en individuel bedømmelse for at se yderligere detaljer om samtalen "
"og bedømmelsen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:136
msgid "Hide individual ratings"
msgstr "Skjul individuelle bedømmelser"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:138
msgid ""
"Ratings are set to be published by default. However, individual ratings can "
"be manually selected to be hidden from the public. The rating is still "
"included in internal reports, and can still be viewed by internal teams. "
"However, public website visitors and portal users do not have access."
msgstr ""
"Bedømmelser er indstillet til at blive publiceret som standard. Dog kan "
"individuelle bedømmelser manuelt vælges til at være skjult for "
"offentligheden. Bedømmelsen er stadig inkluderet i interne rapporter og kan "
"stadig ses af interne teams. Dog har offentlige hjemmesidebesøgende og "
"portalbrugere ikke adgang."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:142
msgid ""
"To hide a rating, go to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Report --> "
"Customer Ratings`. Click on the Kanban card for the rating to be hidden. On "
"the individual rating's detail page, check the box "
"labeled :guilabel:`Visible Internally Only`."
msgstr ""
"For at skjule en bedømmelse skal du gå til :menuselection:`Live Chat-app --> "
"Rapport --> Kundebedømmelser`. Klik på Kanban-kortet for den bedømmelse, der "
"skal skjules. På den enkelte bedømmelses detaljeside skal du markere "
"afkrydsningsfeltet :guilabel:`Kun synlig internt`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of an individual rating's detail page with the visible internally "
"setting checked."
msgstr ""
"Visning af en individuel bedømmelses detaljeside med indstillingen kun "
"synlig internt markeret."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:150
msgid ":doc:`/applications/websites/livechat`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/websites/livechat`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:151
msgid ":doc:`responses`"
msgstr ":doc:`responses`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:152
msgid ":doc:`/applications/websites/website`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/websites/website`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:3
msgid "Reports"
msgstr "Rapporter"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo **Live Chat** includes several reports that allow for the monitoring of "
"operator performance and the identification of trends in customer "
"conversations."
msgstr ""
"Odoo **Live Chat** inkluderer flere rapporter, der giver mulighed for at "
"overvåge operatørpræstationer og identificere tendenser i kundesamtaler."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:8
msgid "The following reports are included in the **Live Chat** app:"
msgstr "Følgende rapporter er inkluderet i **Live Chat**-appen:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:10
msgid ":ref:`Sessions History <livechat/sessions-history>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Sessionsoversigt <livechat/sessions-history>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:11
msgid ":ref:`Session Statistics <livechat/session-statistics>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Sessionsstatistikker <livechat/session-statistics>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:12
msgid ":ref:`Operator Analysis <livechat/operator-analysis>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Operatøranalyse <livechat/operator-analysis>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:15
msgid ""
"The *Live Chat Ratings Report* can also be accessed through "
"the :guilabel:`Report` menu. For more information on this report, and on the "
"**Live Chat** rating process, see :doc:`Live Chat Ratings <../livechat/"
"ratings>`."
msgstr ""
"*Live Chat-bedømmelsesrapporten* kan også tilgås via menuen "
":guilabel:`Rapport`. For mere information om denne rapport og om **Live "
"Chat**-bedømmelsesprocessen, se :doc:`Live Chat-bedømmelser <../livechat/"
"ratings>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:19
msgid ""
"To access a drop-down menu of all the available reports, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Report`."
msgstr ""
"For at få adgang til en rullemenu med alle tilgængelige rapporter skal du "
"navigere til :menuselection:`Live Chat-app --> Rapport`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:25
msgid "Sessions History"
msgstr "Samtalehistorik"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:27
msgid ""
"The *Sessions History* report displays an overview of live chat sessions, "
"including session dates, participant name and country, session duration, the "
"number of messages, and the rating. It also provides access to the complete "
"transcripts of live chat sessions."
msgstr ""
"*Sessionsoversigts*-rapporten viser en oversigt over live chat-sessioner, "
"herunder sessionsdatoer, deltagerens navn og land, sessionsvarighed, "
"antallet af beskeder og bedømmelsen. Den giver også adgang til komplette "
"udskrifter af live chat-sessioner."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:31
msgid ""
"To access this report, navigate to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Report "
"--> Sessions History`. Each live chat session is represented by a Kanban "
"card."
msgstr ""
"For at få adgang til denne rapport skal du navigere til :menuselection:`Live "
"Chat-app --> Rapport --> Sessionsoversigt`. Hver live chat-session er "
"repræsenteret af et Kanban-kort."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:None
msgid "Example of the Sessions History report from the Live Chat application."
msgstr "Eksempel på sessionsoversigtsrapporten fra Live Chat-applikationen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:37
msgid ""
"To view the transcript from a specific session, click the Kanban card. This "
"opens the *Discuss* thread for the conversation."
msgstr ""
"For at se udskriften fra en bestemt session skal du klikke på Kanban-kortet. "
"Dette åbner *Beskeder*-tråden for samtalen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:40
msgid ""
"In the *Discuss* thread, the conversation view displays the entire "
"transcript of the conversation. If the visitor left a rating, it is included "
"at the end of the transcript."
msgstr ""
"I *Beskeder*-tråden viser samtalevisningen hele udskriften af samtalen. Hvis "
"besøgende efterlod en bedømmelse, er den inkluderet i slutningen af "
"udskriften."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:None
msgid "View of the chat transcript in the Discuss application."
msgstr "Visning af chatudskriften i Beskeder-applikationen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:47
msgid "Export sessions history"
msgstr "Eksporter sessionsoversigt"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:49
msgid ""
"The information in this report can be exported, or inserted into a "
"spreadsheet."
msgstr ""
"Informationen i denne rapport kan eksporteres eller indsættes i et regneark."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:51
msgid ""
"On the *Sessions History* report, click the :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :guilabel:`(List)` icon to switch to list view. Next, click "
"the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(gear)` icon to the right of "
"the :guilabel:`History` page title to reveal a drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"På *Sessionsoversigts*-rapporten skal du klikke på :icon:`oi-view-list` "
":guilabel:`(Liste)`-ikonet for at skifte til listevisning. Klik derefter på "
":icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(tandhjul)`-ikonet til højre for sidetitlen "
":guilabel:`Oversigt` for at åbne en rullemenu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:55
msgid ""
"From the drop-down menu, click :guilabel:`Export All` to export all sessions "
"to a spreadsheet, or :guilabel:`Insert list in spreadsheet` to insert the "
"information in a new, or existing, spreadsheet."
msgstr ""
"Z rozbalovací nabídky klikněte na :guilabel:`Exportovat vše`, abyste "
"exportovali všechny relace do tabulky, nebo na :guilabel:`Vložit seznam do "
"tabulky`, abyste vložili informace do nové nebo existující tabulky."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:58
msgid ""
"To only export select sessions, first select the desired sessions to be "
"exported from the list, by clicking the checkbox to the left of each "
"individual session. With the sessions selected, click the :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Actions` icon at the top of the page, and "
"click :guilabel:`Export` or :guilabel:`Insert list in spreadsheet`."
msgstr ""
"Chcete-li exportovat pouze vybrané relace, nejprve vyberte požadované relace "
"ze seznamu kliknutím na zaškrtávací políčko vlevo od každé jednotlivé "
"relace. S vybranými relacemi klikněte na ikonu :icon:`fa-cog` "
":guilabel:`Akce` v horní části stránky a klikněte na :guilabel:`Exportovat` "
"nebo :guilabel:`Vložit seznam do tabulky`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:66
msgid "Session Statistics"
msgstr "Sessionsstatistikker"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:68
msgid ""
"The *Session Statistics* report provides a statistical overview of live chat "
"sessions. The default view for this report displays sessions grouped by the "
"date of creation."
msgstr ""
"Sestava *Statistika relací* poskytuje statistický přehled relací živého "
"chatu. Výchozí zobrazení této sestavy zobrazuje relace seskupené podle data "
"vytvoření."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:71
msgid ""
"To access this report, navigate to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Reports "
"--> Session Statistics`."
msgstr ""
"Pro přístup k této sestavě přejděte na :menuselection:`Live Chat --> "
"Sestavy --> Statistika relací`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:77
msgid ""
"Example of the Sessions Statistics report from the Live Chat application."
msgstr "Příklad sestavy Statistika relací z aplikace Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:77
msgid ""
"The stacked bar graph view of the *Session Statistics* report, with results "
"grouped by Creation Date (hour), then by rating."
msgstr ""
"Zobrazení skládaného sloupcového grafu sestavy *Statistika relací* s "
"výsledky seskupenými podle data vytvoření (hodina) a poté podle hodnocení."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:80
#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:112
msgid ""
"To view a different measure, click the :guilabel:`Measures` drop-down menu "
"at the top-left of the report. The measures available for this report "
"include:"
msgstr ""
"Pro zobrazení jiné míry klikněte na rozbalovací nabídku :guilabel:`Míry` v "
"levém horním rohu sestavy. Dostupné míry pro tuto sestavu zahrnují:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:83
msgid ":guilabel:`# of speakers`: number of participants in the conversation."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Počet účastníků`: počet účastníků v konverzaci."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:84
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Days of activity`: number of days since the operator's first "
"session."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Dny aktivity`: počet dní od první relace operátora."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:85
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Duration of Session (min)`: the duration of a conversation, in "
"minutes."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Délka relace (min)`: délka konverzace v minutách."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:86
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Is visitor anonymous`: denotes whether the conversation "
"participant is anonymous."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Je návštěvník anonymní`: označuje, zda je účastník konverzace "
"anonymní."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:87
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Messages per session`: the total number of messages sent in a "
"conversation. This measure is included in the default view."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Zpráv na relaci`: celkový počet zpráv odeslaných v konverzaci. "
"Tato míra je zahrnuta ve výchozím zobrazení."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:89
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Rating`: the rating received by an operator at the end of a "
"session, if one was provided."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Hodnocení`: hodnocení obdržené operátorem na konci relace, pokud "
"bylo poskytnuto."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:91
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Session not rated`: denotes if a session did **not** receive a "
"rating at the end of the conversation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Relace neohodnocena`: označuje, zda relace **neobdržela** "
"hodnocení na konci konverzace."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:93
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Time to answer (sec)`: the average time, in seconds, before an "
"operator responds to a chat request."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Čas do odpovědi (sek)`: průměrný čas v sekundách, než operátor "
"odpoví na požadavek chatu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:95
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Visitor is Happy`: denotes whether a positive rating was "
"provided. If the visitor gave either a negative or neutral rating, they are "
"considered *unhappy*."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Návštěvník je spokojený`: označuje, zda bylo poskytnuto kladné "
"hodnocení. Pokud návštěvník poskytl záporné nebo neutrální hodnocení, je "
"považován za *nespokojený*."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:97
#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:121
msgid ":guilabel:`Count`: the total number of sessions."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Počet`: celkový počet relací."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:102
msgid "Operator Analysis"
msgstr "Operatøranalyse"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:104
msgid ""
"The *Operator Analysis* report is used to monitor the performance of "
"individual live chat operators."
msgstr ""
"Sestava *Analýza operátorů* se používá ke sledování výkonu jednotlivých "
"operátorů živého chatu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:106
msgid ""
"To access the report, navigate to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Reports "
"--> Operator Analysis`."
msgstr ""
"Pro přístup k sestavě přejděte na :menuselection:`Live Chat --> Sestavy --> "
"Analýza operátorů`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:108
msgid ""
"The default view for this report is a bar chart, which only displays "
"conversations from the current month, as indicated by the :guilabel:`This "
"Month` default search filter. Conversations are grouped by operator."
msgstr ""
"Výchozí zobrazení této sestavy je sloupcový graf, který zobrazuje pouze "
"konverzace z aktuálního měsíce, jak je uvedeno výchozím vyhledávacím filtrem "
":guilabel:`Tento měsíc`. Konverzace jsou seskupeny podle operátora."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:115
msgid ""
":guilabel:`# of Sessions`: the number of sessions an operator participated "
"in. This measure is included by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`# af sessioner`: antallet af sessioner, som en operatør har "
"deltaget i. Denne måling er inkluderet som standard."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:117
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Average duration`: the average duration of a conversation, in "
"seconds."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Gennemsnitlig varighed`: den gennemsnitlige varighed af en "
"samtale i sekunder."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:118
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Average rating`: the average rating received by the operator."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Gennemsnitlig bedømmelse`: den gennemsnitlige bedømmelse modtaget "
"af operatøren."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:119
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Time to answer`: the average amount of time before the operator "
"responds to a chat request, in seconds."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tid til at svare`: den gennemsnitlige tid, før operatøren svarer "
"på en chatanmodning, i sekunder."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:None
msgid "Example of the Operator Analysis report from the Live Chat application."
msgstr "Eksempel på rapporten Operatøranalyse fra Live Chat-applikationen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:3
msgid "Commands and canned responses"
msgstr "Kommandoer og færdige svar"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:5
msgid ""
"In the Odoo **Live Chat** application, *commands* allow the user to perform "
"specific actions both inside the chat window, and through other Odoo "
"applications. The **Live Chat** app also includes *canned responses*. These "
"are customized, preconfigured substitutions that allow users to replace "
"shortcut entries in place of longer, well-thought out responses to some of "
"the most common questions and comments."
msgstr ""
"I Odoo **Live Chat**-applikationen giver *kommandoer* brugeren mulighed for "
"at udføre specifikke handlinger både inde i chatvinduet og gennem andre Odoo-"
"applikationer. **Live Chat**-appen indeholder også *færdige svar*. Disse er "
"tilpassede, præ-konfigurerede erstatninger, der gør det muligt for brugere "
"at erstatte genvejsindtastninger i stedet for længere, gennemtænkte svar på "
"nogle af de mest almindelige spørgsmål og kommentarer."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:11
msgid ""
"Both commands and canned responses save time, and allow users to maintain a "
"level of consistency throughout their conversations."
msgstr ""
"Både kommandoer og færdige svar sparer tid og giver brugerne mulighed for at "
"opretholde et niveau af konsistens gennem deres samtaler."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:15
msgid "Execute a command"
msgstr "Udfør en kommando"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:17
msgid ""
"Live chat *commands* are keywords that trigger preconfigured actions. When a "
"live chat *operator* is participating in a conversation with a customer or "
"website visitor, they can execute a command by typing `/`, followed by the "
"command."
msgstr ""
"Live chat-*kommandoer* er nøgleord, der udløser præ-konfigurerede "
"handlinger. Når en live chat-*operatør* deltager i en samtale med en kunde "
"eller hjemmesidebesøgende, kan de udføre en kommando ved at skrive `/` "
"efterfulgt af kommandoen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:21
msgid ""
"Commands, and the resulting actions, are only visible in the conversation "
"window for the live chat operator. A customer does not see any commands that "
"an operator uses in a conversation from their view of the chat."
msgstr ""
"Kommandoer og de resulterende handlinger er kun synlige i samtalevinduet for "
"live chat-operatøren. En kunde ser ikke nogen kommandoer, som en operatør "
"bruger i en samtale fra deres visning af chatten."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:26
msgid ""
"During a conversation with a customer, a live chat operator executes the "
"command to :ref:`create a ticket <live-chat/ticket>`. After entering the "
"command, `/ticket`, the system automatically creates a ticket with the "
"information from the conversation. It also includes a link to the new "
"ticket, so the operator can go there directly to add any additional "
"information, if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Under en samtale med en kunde udfører en live chat-operatør kommandoen til "
"at :ref:`oprette en sag <live-chat/ticket>`. Efter indtastning af kommandoen "
"`/ticket` opretter systemet automatisk en sag med informationerne fra "
"samtalen. Den inkluderer også et link til den nye sag, så operatøren kan gå "
"der direkte for at tilføje yderligere information, hvis det er nødvendigt."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:34
msgid "More information about each available command can be found below."
msgstr "Flere oplysninger om hver tilgængelig kommando kan findes nedenfor."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:37
msgid "Help"
msgstr "Hjælp"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:39
msgid ""
"If an operator types `/help` in the chat window, an informative message that "
"includes the potential entry types an operator can make is displayed."
msgstr ""
"Hvis en operatør skriver `/help` i chatvinduet, vises en informativ "
"meddelelse, der inkluderer de potentielle indtastningstyper, en operatør kan "
"foretage."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:42
msgid ""
"Type `@username` to mention a user in the conversation. A notification will "
"be sent to that user's inbox or email, depending on their notification "
"settings."
msgstr ""
"Skriv `@brugernavn` for at nævne en bruger i samtalen. En meddelelse vil "
"blive sendt til den pågældende brugers indbakke eller e-mail, afhængigt af "
"deres meddelelsesindstillinger."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:44
msgid "Type `/command` to execute a command."
msgstr "Skriv `/kommando` for at udføre en kommando."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:45
msgid ""
"Type `:shortcut` to insert a :ref:`canned response <live-chat/canned-"
"responses>`."
msgstr ""
"Skriv `:genvej` for at indsætte et :ref:`færdigt svar <live-chat/canned-"
"responses>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:48
msgid ":doc:`/applications/productivity/discuss`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/productivity/discuss`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:49
msgid ":doc:`/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:52
msgid "Ticket & search tickets"
msgstr "Sag & søg sager"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:54
msgid ""
"The `/ticket` and `/search_tickets` commands allow operators to create "
"helpdesk tickets directly from a conversation, and search through existing "
"tickets by keyword or ticket number."
msgstr ""
"Kommandoerne `/ticket` og `/search_tickets` giver operatører mulighed for at "
"oprette kundeservicebilletter direkte fra en samtale og søge gennem "
"eksisterende billetter efter søgeord eller billetnummer."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:58
msgid ""
"The `/ticket` and `/search_tickets` commands can **only** be used if the "
"**Helpdesk** app has been installed, and *Live Chat* has been activated on a "
"*Helpdesk* team. To activate *Live Chat*, go to :menuselection:`Helpdesk app "
"--> Configuration --> Helpdesk Teams`, and select a team. Scroll to "
"the :guilabel:`Channels` section, and check the box labeled, :guilabel:`Live "
"Chat`."
msgstr ""
"Kommandoerne `/ticket` og `/search_tickets` kan **kun** bruges, hvis "
"**Kundeservice**-appen er blevet installeret, og *Live Chat* er blevet "
"aktiveret på et *Kundeservice*-team. For at aktivere *Live Chat* skal du gå "
"til :menuselection:`Kundeservice-app --> Konfiguration --> "
"Kundeserviceteams` og vælge et team. Rul ned til sektionen "
":guilabel:`Kanaler` og markér afkrydsningsfeltet mærket :guilabel:`Live "
"Chat`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:66
msgid "Create a ticket from a live chat"
msgstr "Opret en billet fra en live chat"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:68
msgid ""
"If an operator types `/ticket` in the chat window, the conversation is used "
"to create a *Helpdesk* ticket."
msgstr ""
"Hvis en operatør skriver `/ticket` i chatvinduet, bruges samtalen til at "
"oprette en *Kundeservice*-billet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:71
msgid ""
"After entering the `/ticket` command, type a title for the ticket into the "
"chat window, then press `Enter`."
msgstr ""
"Efter at have indtastet kommandoen `/ticket` skal du skrive en titel til "
"billetten i chatvinduet og derefter trykke på `Enter`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:None
msgid "View of the results from a helpdesk search in a Live Chat conversation."
msgstr ""
"Visning af resultaterne fra en kundeservicesøgning i en Live Chat-samtale."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:77
msgid ""
"The newly created ticket will be added to the *Helpdesk* team that has live "
"chat enabled. If more than one team has live chat enabled, the ticket will "
"automatically be assigned based on the team's priority."
msgstr ""
"Den nyoprettede billet vil blive tilføjet til det *Kundeservice*-team, der "
"har live chat aktiveret. Hvis mere end ét team har live chat aktiveret, vil "
"billetten automatisk blive tildelt baseret på teamets prioritet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:81
msgid ""
"The transcript from the conversation will be added to the new ticket, under "
"the :guilabel:`Description` tab."
msgstr ""
"Udskriften fra samtalen vil blive tilføjet til den nye billet under fanen "
":guilabel:`Beskrivelse`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:84
msgid ""
"To access the new ticket, click on the link in the chat window, or go to "
"the :menuselection:`Helpdesk app` and click the :guilabel:`Tickets` button "
"on the Kanban card for the appropriate team."
msgstr ""
"For at få adgang til den nye billet skal du klikke på linket i chatvinduet "
"eller gå til :menuselection:`Kundeservice-app` og klikke på knappen "
":guilabel:`Billetter` på Kanban-kortet for det relevante team."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:89
msgid "Search for a ticket from a live chat"
msgstr "Søg efter en billet fra en live chat"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:91
msgid ""
"If an operator types `/search_tickets` in the chat window, they can search "
"through *Helpdesk* tickets, either by ticket number or keyword."
msgstr ""
"Hvis en operatør skriver `/search_tickets` i chatvinduet, kan de søge gennem "
"*Kundeservice*-billetter, enten efter billetnummer eller søgeord."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:94
msgid ""
"After entering the `/search_tickets` command, type a keyword or ticket "
"number, then press :kbd:`Enter`. If one or more related tickets are found, a "
"list of links is generated in the conversation window."
msgstr ""
"Efter at have indtastet kommandoen `/search_tickets` skal du skrive et "
"søgeord eller billetnummer og derefter trykke på :kbd:`Enter`. Hvis en eller "
"flere relaterede billetter findes, genereres en liste med links i "
"samtalevinduet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:102
msgid ""
"Results from the search command will only be seen by the operator, not the "
"customer."
msgstr ""
"Resultater fra søgekommandoen vil kun blive set af operatøren, ikke af "
"kunden."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:105
msgid "History"
msgstr "Historik"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:107
msgid ""
"If an operator types `/history` in the chat window, it generates a list of "
"the most recent pages the visitor has viewed on the website (up to 15)."
msgstr ""
"Hvis en operatør skriver `/history` i chatvinduet, genererer det en liste "
"over de seneste sider, som besøgende har set på hjemmesiden (op til 15)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of the results from a /history command in a Live Chat conversation."
msgstr ""
"Visning af resultaterne fra en /history-kommando i en Live Chat-samtale."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:114
msgid "Lead"
msgstr "Kundeemne"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:116
msgid ""
"By typing `/lead` in the chat window, an operator can create a *lead* in the "
"**CRM** application."
msgstr ""
"Ved at skrive `/lead` i chatvinduet kan en operatør oprette et *kundeemne* i "
"**CRM**-applikationen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:None
msgid "View of the results from a /lead command in a Live Chat conversation."
msgstr "Visning af resultaterne fra en /lead-kommando i en Live Chat-samtale."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:122
msgid ""
"The `/lead` command can only be used if the **CRM** app has been installed."
msgstr ""
"Kommandoen `/lead` kan kun bruges, hvis **CRM**-appen er blevet installeret."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:124
msgid ""
"After typing `/lead`, create a title for this new lead, then press `Enter`. "
"A link with the lead title appears. Click the link, or navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`CRM` app to view the :guilabel:`Pipeline`."
msgstr ""
"Efter at have skrevet `/lead` skal du oprette en titel til dette nye "
"kundeemne og derefter trykke på `Enter`. Et link med kundeemnetitlen vises. "
"Klik på linket, eller navigér til :menuselection:`CRM`-appen for at se "
":guilabel:`Pipeline`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:129
msgid ""
"The link to the new lead can only be seen and accessed by the operator, not "
"the customer."
msgstr ""
"Linket til det nye kundeemne kan kun ses og tilgås af operatøren, ikke af "
"kunden."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:131
msgid ""
"The transcript of that specific live chat conversation (where the lead was "
"created) is added to the :guilabel:`Internal Notes` tab of the lead form."
msgstr ""
"Přepis tohoto konkrétního rozhovoru v živém chatu (kde byl vytvořen "
"potenciální zákazník) je přidán na kartu :guilabel:`Interní poznámky` "
"formuláře potenciálního zákazníka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:134
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Extra Information` tab of the lead form, "
"the :guilabel:`Source` will be listed as :guilabel:`Livechat`."
msgstr ""
"Na kartě :guilabel:`Extra informace` formuláře potenciálního zákazníka bude "
"jako :guilabel:`Zdroj` uvedeno :guilabel:`Livechat`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:138
msgid "Leave"
msgstr "Forlad"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:140
msgid ""
"If an operator types `/leave` in the chat window, they can automatically "
"exit the conversation. This command does not cause the customer to be "
"removed from the conversation, nor does it automatically end the "
"conversation."
msgstr ""
"Pokud operátor napíše `/leave` v okně chatu, může automaticky opustit "
"konverzaci. Tento příkaz nezpůsobí odstranění zákazníka z konverzace, ani "
"automaticky neukončí konverzaci."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:145
msgid ":doc:`/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:146
msgid ":doc:`../../services/helpdesk`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../services/helpdesk`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:151
msgid "Canned responses"
msgstr "Klargjorte svar"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:153
msgid ""
"*Canned responses* are customizable inputs where a *shortcut* stands in for "
"a longer response. An operator will enter the shortcut, and it is "
"automatically replaced by the expanded *substitution* response in the "
"conversation."
msgstr ""
"*Přednastavené odpovědi* jsou přizpůsobitelné vstupy, kde *zkratka* "
"zastupuje delší odpověď. Operátor zadá zkratku a ta je automaticky nahrazena "
"rozšířenou *substitucí* odpovědi v konverzaci."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:158
msgid "Create canned responses"
msgstr "Vytvořit přednastavené odpovědi"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:160
msgid ""
"To create a new canned response, go to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> "
"Configuration --> Canned Responses --> New`."
msgstr ""
"Pro vytvoření nové přednastavené odpovědi přejděte na :menuselection:`Live "
"Chat aplikace --> Konfigurace --> Přednastavené odpovědi --> Nový`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:163
msgid ""
"Type a shortcut command in the :guilabel:`Shortcut` field. Next, click "
"the :guilabel:`Substitution` field, and type the message that should replace "
"the shortcut."
msgstr ""
"Napište příkaz zkratky do pole :guilabel:`Zkratka`. Dále klikněte na pole "
":guilabel:`Substituce` a napište zprávu, která má zkratku nahradit."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:167
msgid ""
"Try to connect the shortcut to the topic of the substitution. The easier it "
"is for the operators to remember, the easier it is to use the canned "
"responses in conversations."
msgstr ""
"Snažte se propojit zkratku s tématem substituce. Čím snazší je pro operátory "
"si ji zapamatovat, tím snazší je používat přednastavené odpovědi v "
"konverzacích."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:171
msgid "Authorized groups"
msgstr "Autorizované skupiny"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:173
msgid ""
"When a new canned response is created, it can **only** be utilized by the "
"operator that created it. To allow the response to be used by other "
"operators, select one or more :ref:`groups <access-rights/groups>` from "
"the :guilabel:`Authorized Groups` drop-down list."
msgstr ""
"Když je vytvořena nová přednastavená odpověď, může ji využívat **pouze** "
"operátor, který ji vytvořil. Aby mohla být odpověď použita i jinými "
"operátory, vyberte jednu nebo více :ref:`skupin <access-rights/groups>` z "
"rozbalovacího seznamu :guilabel:`Autorizované skupiny`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:178
msgid "Use canned responses in a live chat conversation"
msgstr "Použít přednastavené odpovědi v konverzaci živého chatu"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:180
msgid ""
"To use a canned response in a conversation, click the :icon:`fa-plus-"
"circle` :guilabel:`(plus)` icon in the message window. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Insert a Canned Response`. This opens a list of available "
"canned responses. Either select a response from the list, or type the "
"appropriate shortcut, then click the :icon:`fa-paper-"
"plane` :guilabel:`(send)` icon or hit :kbd:`Enter`."
msgstr ""
"Pro použití přednastavené odpovědi v konverzaci klikněte na ikonu :icon:`fa-"
"plus-circle` :guilabel:`(plus)` v okně zprávy. Poté klikněte na "
":guilabel:`Vložit přednastavenou odpověď`. Otevře se seznam dostupných "
"přednastavených odpovědí. Buď vyberte odpověď ze seznamu, nebo napište "
"příslušnou zkratku, poté klikněte na ikonu :icon:`fa-paper-plane` :guilabel:`"
"(odeslat)` nebo stiskněte :kbd:`Enter`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:186
msgid ""
"Typing `::` into a chat window on its own generates a list of available "
"canned responses. Responses can be manually selected from the list, in "
"addition to the use of shortcuts."
msgstr ""
"Napsání `::` do okna chatu samostatně vygeneruje seznam dostupných "
"přednastavených odpovědí. Odpovědi lze ručně vybrat ze seznamu kromě použití "
"zkratek."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:0
msgid "View of a chat window and the list of available canned responses."
msgstr "Zobrazení okna chatu a seznamu dostupných přednastavených odpovědí."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website.rst:7
msgid "Website"
msgstr "Hjemmeside"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website.rst:9
msgid ""
"**Odoo Website** offers a user-friendly platform for creating and managing "
"your website. It includes various tools and features to help you design, "
"publish, and maintain web pages without needing advanced technical skills. "
"You can easily customize layouts, add multimedia content, and integrate with "
"other Odoo apps to expand your website's functionality."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo Website** nabízí uživatelsky přívětivou platformu pro vytváření a "
"správu vašich webových stránek. Zahrnuje různé nástroje a funkce, které vám "
"pomohou navrhovat, publikovat a udržovat webové stránky bez potřeby "
"pokročilých technických dovedností. Můžete snadno přizpůsobit rozvržení, "
"přidat multimediální obsah a integrovat s dalšími aplikacemi Odoo pro "
"rozšíření funkčnosti vašich webových stránek."

