#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:119
msgid "Add an Odoo contact form on a non-Odoo website"
msgstr "Tilføj en Odoo-kontaktformular på en ikke-Odoo-hjemmeside"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:121
msgid ""
"You can display an Odoo contact form on another website using an iframe. To "
"do so, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Du kan vise en Odoo-kontaktformular på en anden hjemmeside ved hjælp af en "
"iframe. For at gøre dette, følg disse trin:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:124
msgid ""
"**Prepare the Odoo form:** Create a contact form on a page in Odoo Website "
"and remove the :ref:`header design <website/header_footer/header-design>` "
"and the :ref:`footer design <website/header_footer/footer-design>`. Make "
"sure only the contact form remains on the page."
msgstr ""
"**Forbered Odoo-formularen:** Opret en kontaktformular på en side i Odoo "
"Hjemmeside og fjern :ref:`header-designet <website/header_footer/header-"
"design>` og :ref:`footer-designet <website/header_footer/footer-design>`. "
"Sørg for at kun kontaktformularen forbliver på siden."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:127
msgid ""
"**Generate an embeddable code:** Copy the URL of the Odoo form page and "
"paste it into an iframe generator, such as `La Digitale.dev <https://"
"ladigitale.dev/digitools/generateur-iframe>`_ or `iFrame Generator <https://"
"www.iframe-generator.com/>`_ . Adjust the width and height for proper "
"display."
msgstr ""
"**Generér en indlejrbar kode:** Kopiér URL'en til Odoo-formularsiden og "
"indsæt den i en iframe-generator, såsom `La Digitale.dev <https://"
"ladigitale.dev/digitools/generateur-iframe>`_ eller `iFrame Generator "
"<https://www.iframe-generator.com/>`_. Justér bredde og højde for korrekt "
"visning."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:131
msgid ""
"**Add the embedded code to the non-Odoo website:** Open the relevant page’s "
"HTML (in the code editor or CMS) and insert the embedded code where the form "
"should be displayed."
msgstr ""
"**Tilføj den indlejrede kode til den ikke-Odoo-hjemmeside:** Åbn den "
"relevante sides HTML (i kodeeditoren eller CMS'et) og indsæt den indlejrede "
"kode, hvor formularen skal vises."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:135
msgid "Example of an embedded code:"
msgstr "Eksempel på en indlejret kode:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/building_blocks.rst:155
