#~ msgstr ""
#~ "**Medie**: Kanal brugt til at dele (levere) dit link (f.eks. en email "
#~ "eller en Facebook reklame)."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "**Source**: platform where the traffic originates (e.g. Google or "
