#~ msgid ""
#~ "The sitemap points out pages to index to search engine robots. Odoo "
#~ "generates a ``/sitemap.xml`` file automatically for you. For performance "
#~ "reasons, this file is cached and updated every 12 hours."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Sitemappet udpeger sider til indeksering for søgemaskine robotter. Odoo "
#~ "generere en ``/sitemap.xml`` fil automatisk for dig. Af hensyn til "
#~ "ydeevne, lagres og opdateres denne fil hver 12. time."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "By default, all URLs will be in a single ``/sitemap.xml`` file, but if "
#~ "you have a lot of pages, Odoo will automatically create a Sitemap Index "
#~ "file, respecting the `sitemaps.org protocol <http://www.sitemaps.org/"
#~ "protocol.html>`__ grouping sitemap URL's in 45000 chunks per file."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Per standard vil alle URL være i én enkelt ``/sitemap.xml`` fil, men hvis "
